Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hari itsinda ry'abarwaye indwara ya Pneumonia y'impamvu itaramenyekana ryamenyekanye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu Ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko umuganga w'indwara ari coronavirus nshya ubu yitwa coronavirus acute respiratory syndrome 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yiswe indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, byagaragaye ko hafi 80% by'abantu barwaye COVID-19 barwaye indwara yoroheje, urugero nk'indwara y'ubuhumekero, hamwe n'indwara y'ibihaha cyangwa ntayo, kandi abenshi muri abo barwayi barakira.
Mu bantu bagera kuri 14%, COVID-19 ikomeza iba ndwara ikomeye cyane igasaba kuvurwa mu bitaro mu gihe abasigaye 6% baba barwaye cyane bagasaba kwitabwaho.
Imfu z'abarwayi bavurirwa mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye uko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwagiye bufata indi ntera muri buri gihugu cy'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) n'Ubwongereza (UK) ndetse tugereranya ibyo bihugu n'Intara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Twagereranyije kandi imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza n'iyo mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yongeye kwiyongera mu by'ubutaka ndetse n'imiterere y'icyorezo cya COVID-19 ku isi yose muri iki gihe, hakurikijwe imiterere y'ibihugu.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu nomero yo ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020 ya Eurosurveillance, Spiteri et al. batangaje ko ari bwo bwa mbere COVID-19 yemejwe mu Burayi nk'uko byemezwa na WHO.
Muri EU/EEA, abarwayi batatu ba mbere bemejwe batangajwe n'u Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bagarutse bavuye i Wuhan, mu Ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, hari abantu banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu byose 30 bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza (UK), aho hagati y'itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 no muri uwo munsi, abantu 39,768 banduye n'abantu 1,727 bapfuye, hamwe n'abantu 17,750 banduye n'abantu 1,441 bapfuye mu Butaliyani honyine.
Kubona imibare yose hamwe n'ibimenyetso byose by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurwanya Indwara (ECDC), imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi, ituruka gusa ku makuru yemewe nk'ibiro by'ubuzima by'icyo gihugu, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'akarere ndetse na OMS, iherutse kuvugururwa buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma uko COVID-19 iteye mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK, ndetse no kugereranya ayo makuru n'ayo mu Butaliyani.
Mu rwego rwo gufatira mu gaciro ikwirakwira ry'abanduye COVID-19, twabaze imibare y'ibyumweru 14 bya nyuma by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19, bityo dufata mu mutwe inzira kamere ya COVID-19, muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA na UK, mu gihe cy'itariki ya 1 Mutarama15 Werurwe 2020.
Nanone kandi, twerekanye imibare y'abanduye muri buri gihugu ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo ugereranyije n'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
Imiterere ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Imiterere y'ibyumweru 14 bya mbere by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK muri rusange ikurikirana imiterere y'intara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Ku baturage bose bo muri EU/EEA n'ab'Ubwongereza, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma buzamuka cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Ibindi bisobanuro).
Ibi ahanini byatewe n'izamuka ryihuse ry'umubare w'abanduye batangajwe baturutse mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byerekana ko habayeho kuzamuka nk'uko mu mubare w'abanduye COVID-19 (Ibindi).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK ugereranyije n'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Yashimangiye ko, ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ibindi bihugu 15 bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byari byatangaje umubare w'abanduye ungana n'uwa Italy mu byumweru 3 gusa bishize cyangwa munsi yayo.
Ibisubizo byacu byerekana ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 ugenda wiyongera cyane muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Imiterere y'ibyabaye muri COVID-19 igaragaza ko icyorezo cyandura ku muvuduko umwe mu bihugu byose.
Nubwo ibihugu biri ku rwego rutandukanye, itandukaniro mu bisubizo by'ubuzima rusange by'igihugu n'ibisobanuro by'ubwandu bishobora gutandukana mu bihugu bitandukanye ndetse n'amabwiriza atandukanye yo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa ku bw'igaragazwa rya COVID-19, harimo no gupimwa nyuma.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu ntara z'u Butaliyani zagize ikibazo cyo kubona 10% by'abarwayi banduye COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho mu buryo bwihuse, kandi ibitangazamakuru byavuze ko ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi mu karere byamaze kugera ku gipimo cyabyo.
Amakuru ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu bigo byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 ubu aboneka ku rwego rwa EU/EEA ku bantu 6% na 1% gusa (amakuru ntaragaragazwa).
Icyakora, ibyo bisobanuro bigomba gukusanywa mu buryo bufite gahunda kugira ngo bishyigikire amakuru y'ubugenzuzi bugenda bukorwa yibanda ku mubare w'abanduye n'abapfa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 bugaragaza itandukaniro rinini mu bijyanye no kubona ibitanda byo kwivuza no kwita ku barwayi bo hagati mu Burayi, hagati ya 29.2 mu Budage na 4.2 ku baturage 100,000 muri Portugal.
Ibi bivuze ko igihugu gifite ibikoresho byinshi cyangwa bike ugereranyije n'Ubutaliyani (12.5 ibitanda byo kwivuza no kwita ku barwayi bo hagati kuri 100,000 mu baturage muri 201011).
Ibipimo by'ikoranabuhanga bijyanye n'ubwiyongere bw'ubushobozi mu kwivuza, hamwe n'ibyerekezwa kuri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza by'ubwiyongere bw'abanduye COVID-19 bari mu bitaro bifitanye isano na > 90% by'ibyago byo kurenza ubushobozi bw'ibitanda byo kwivuza, byatanzwe mu ivugurura rya gatandatu ry'igeragezwa ryihuse ry'ibyago bya COVID-19 na ECDC.
Kubera ko kugeza ubu, ubwandu bwiganje mu turere tumwe na tumwe tw'ibihugu bya EU/EEA na UK, ndetse ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi ba majonjora bikunze gukorana n'abaturage bagizwe n'akarere, amakuru y'ubwandu n'ibitanda by'abarwayi ba majonjora yagombye kuboneka muri Tatanama ku bigo by'akarere by'urwego rwa 2 rwa statistike (NUTS-2).
Ubumenyi bw'u Butaliyani n'imiterere iriho mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kirimo gukwirakwira mu buryo bwihuse muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye bigomba rero kwitegura uko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora guhitana abaturage buhoro buhoro no kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abarwayi banduye COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho, cyane cyane ku barwayi bakomeye, nk'uko biri mu ntara z'Ubutaliyani zagize ingaruka.
Nk'uko byashimangiwe mu igenzura ryihuse ry'ibyago bya ECDC, uburyo bwihuse, bwihuse kandi bwuzuye ni ngombwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2, kuva ku buryo bwo kugabanya kugera ku kugabanya, kuko kwitega kwiyongera vuba kw'umubare w'abarwayi bishobora kutaha abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro igihe gihagije cyo gusobanukirwa, kwakira no guhuza ibisubizo byabo neza niba bitakozwe hakiri kare.
Igenzura ryihuse ry'ibyago kandi rirerekana ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari uburyo bugufi ibihugu bishobora gukomeza kongera imbaraga mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya ibibazo by'ubuzima.
Ibi biramutse bitabaye, birashoboka ko izindi sisitemu z'ubuzima z'ibihugu bya EU/EEA zizahura n'umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), kizazira indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,000 no kwandura abantu barenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, bigateza amakuba ku bantu.
Kimwe na virusi ihuriyeho, SARS-CoV, yateje SARS mu bantu babarirwa mu bihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba yakwirakwijwe n'imbeba kandi igateza ibimenyetso nk'ibyo binyuze mu buryo nk'ubwo.
Nyamara, COVID-19 ifite ubukana n'ubwandu buciriritse cyane kurusha SARS ariko yanduza cyane kandi ikagira ingaruka ku bantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko n'abagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'umubare w'ibitabo by'imfashanyigisho byagiye byiyongera ku birebana n'iyo ndwara nshya, iyi ngingo yagerageje gutanga ibitekerezo bihuje n'igihe kandi byimbitse ku birebana n'icyo kibazo cy'ubushakashatsi kigenda kigenda kigaruka mu buryo bwihuse.
Tuzaganira ku by'ibanze by'icyorezo, etiology, virology, gusuzuma, kuvura, kubara no kwirinda indwara.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko iyi raporo izadufasha gusobanukirwa no kurandura iyi ndwara iteza urupfu.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi wabaye ku ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye ikintu kidasanzwe kandi kitazibagirana ku Bashinwa basabwe kuguma mu ngo zabo mu gihe cy'iminsi mikuru ndetse no mu byumweru bikurikiyeho bitewe n'icyorezo cya virusi.
Iyi virusi ifite aho ihuriye cyane na koronavirusi (CoV) yateje icyorezo cya SARS mu 2003; bityo, yiswe SARS-CoV-2 n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020 n'indwara ifitanye isano yitwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, gihita gikwirakwira mu gihugu cyose ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yateje abantu barenga 80,000 banduye COVID-19, abarenga 40,000 barekurwa barataha naho abarenga 3,000 barapfa.
OMS yaburiye ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi wa rubanda wa mbere" kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, inyandiko zirenga 2000 zanditswe kuri COVID-19 zirimo virusi, icyorezo, etiolojiya, gusuzuma no kuvura kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yagaragaje ko virusi yari yaratoranyijwe mu barwayi bamwe na bamwe.
Iyi raporo igerageza gusobanura neza iterambere ry'ubushakashatsi muri icyo gice gishya kandi kizamuka cyane.
Aho bikenewe, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na CoV, indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, yadutse mu 2012).
Tuzaganira kandi ku byo tuzi kugeza ubu ku bijyanye no kwirinda no gusuzuma indwara ndetse n'ibindi bibazo by'ingenzi.
CoV zisanzwe zisanzwe zibonwa nk'indwara zitagira icyo zitwara abantu, akenshi zitera 15% by'ibicurane bisanzwe 4.
Icyakora, muri iki kinyejana, twabonye inshuro ebyiri za CoV z'abantu zanduza cyane, ari zo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatumye habaho ibyorezo by'indwara mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi bidatinze byakwirakwiriye mu bindi bihugu byinshi bifite ubwandu n'urupfu bikabije.
Ku bw'ibyo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu Ishusho ya 1.1, uduhimba tw'indwara ya Pneumonia tudafite inkomoko izwi twabanje kubwirwa i Wuhan ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 ku Kanama gashinzwe ubuzima mu Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, hari hamaze gushyirwa hanze utwo duce duto twa CoV.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020 ni bwo havuzwe umuntu wa mbere wapfuye azize Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu buryo bwihuse mu mijyi, intara n'ibihugu bituranye.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, hari ubwandu mu bakozi b'ubuzima, bigaragaza ko ubwandu bw'abantu bushobora kubaho.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan washyizweho gahunda yo gufunga hamwe na serivisi zose z'ubwikorezi rusange zahagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe ku barwayi b'iyo ndwara bwagaragaje ko mu barwayi 41 bagaragaweho ubwandu, 21 gusa ari bo bahuye mu buryo butaziguye n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan, aho bivugwa ko ari ho indwara yaturutse.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingutu ku isi.
Mu gihe cy'iyi raporo, iki cyorezo cyamaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo cya 2).2).
Kubera ko ibintu bigenda byiyongera mu buryo bwihuse, urugero rw'icyorezo n'uburemere bwacyo ntibiramenyekana.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bigo bitandukanye ku barwayi 8,866 barimo 4,021 banduye COVID-19 bwemeje ko hari ikindi kintu gishya cyabayeho muri iki cyorezo (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yandura abarwayi b'imyaka yose, ariko abenshi muri bo bari hagati y'imyaka 30 na 65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47.7%) cy'abarwayi banduye bari hejuru y'imyaka 50, bake cyane bari munsi y'imyaka 20 kandi abantu 14 gusa banduye bari munsi y'imyaka 10.
