Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku mibare y'abantu mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019 bugaragaza ko igipimo cy'ibimenyetso ari 98% ku ndwara y'umuriro, 76% ku guhumeka, 55% ku guhumeka, na 3% ku ndwara ya diarrhée; 8% by'abarwayi bakeneye ubufasha bwo guhumeka.
