Abarwayi bakunze kugira amapifumo ya atypical, ibikomere by'ibihaha bikomeye na syndrome y'ubuhumekero budafite imbaraga (ARDS).
Iyo ARDS ibayeho, kubyimba bidateganijwe, kwiyongera kw'amazi n'umuvuduko wa fibrosis bigira ingaruka ku mwuka.
Imikorere mibi ya Pneumocytes y'ubwoko bwa I na II igabanya urugero rwa surfactant kandi igatuma habaho umuvuduko w'ubushyuhe, bityo igabanya ubushobozi bw'ibihaha bwo kwaguka kandi igatuma ibyago byo kunanirwa kw'ibihaha byiyongera.
Ku bw'ibyo, kuba radiyo y'agafu igaragaza ko umuntu afite ikibazo cyo mu gatuza akenshi biba bihuje n'uko indwara iri ku kigero cyo hejuru.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, isesengura rya mbere ry'indwara ya COVID-19 ryerekanye ko kwandura kw'imyakura y'ibihaha, kubaho kw'uruhu rwa hyaline no kwinjira kwa za limfozi z'uruhu hamwe n'ingirabuzimafatizo za sinitium z'imikorere myinshi mu bihaha by'abarwayi bapfuye kubera iyo ndwara, bihuye n'indwara z'ubwandu bwa virusi na ARDS ndetse bisa n'indwara z'abarwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Kumenya RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu buryo bwo gusubiza mu buryo bwa RT-PCR (transcription-reverse polymerase chain reaction) byakoreshejwe nk'ingingo y'ingenzi mu gusuzuma COVID-19.
Icyakora, kubera umubare munini w'abatanga ibimenyetso by'ibinyoma, bishobora guteza icyorezo, ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi byatangiye gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma (bitakiri ku buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga rya RT-PCR gusa) mu Bushinwa ku ya 13 Gashyantare 2020.
Ibintu bisa n'ibyo ni na byo byabayeho mu gihe cyo gusuzuma SARS.
Ku bw'ibyo, ihuriro ry'amateka y'uburwayi, ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi, ibizamini byo mu bitaro n'ibyavuye mu mashini z'imashini z'imashini z'imashini z'imashini ni ingenzi kandi ni ngombwa kugira ngo umuntu ashobore kubona indwara neza.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda rya Feng Zhang ryasobanuye prototype ikoresha ubuhanga bwa SHERLOCK bushingiye kuri CRISPR mu gutahura SARS-CoV-2, ikamenya ibice bya SARS-CoV-2 RNA ikora mu 20 × 10-18 mol/L kugeza 200 × 10-18 mol/L (10-100 kopi kuri microlitiro imwe y'ibikoresho) ikoresheje inkingi z'ibishyimbo mu gihe kitarenze isaha idafite ibikoresho bihambaye.
Byitezwe ko ubu buryo bushya bushobora kongera cyane ibyiyumvo n'ubworoherane mu gihe bwaba bwemejwe mu bipimo byo mu buvuzi.
Kubera kubura ubunararibonye mu ndwara ziterwa na CoV nshya, abaganga muri rusange bashobora gutanga ubuvuzi bw'inkunga ku barwayi ba COVID-19, mu gihe bagerageza uburyo butandukanye bwo kuvura bwakoreshejwe cyangwa bwatanzwe mbere yo kuvura izindi CoV nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV ndetse n'izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi (Imbonerahamwe (Imbonerahamwe2).2).
Ubu buryo bwo kuvura burimo ubuvuzi buriho n'ubushobora gutangwa n'imiti ya virusi, imyunyozi, siteroyi, plasma y'abarwayi bakize, imiti y'Abashinwa n'ubufasha mu by'imitekerereze.
Ndetse n'umushongi w'amaraso y'abarwayi bakize, urimo uratangwa kugira ngo ukoreshwe mu kuvura.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuvuzi arimo arashakisha uburyo bwo gukora imiti n'indwara zo kurwanya iyo virusi.
SARS-CoV-2 ikunze gutera ibihaha mu gihe cy'intangiriro kandi ishobora no gutera, ku kigero cyo hasi, izindi ngingo zitanga ACE2, nk'urwego rw'igifu n'impyiko.
Nyamara, kudakora neza no kunanirwa guhumeka ni ikibazo gikomeye ku barwayi kandi ni kimwe mu bituma abantu benshi bapfa.
Ku bw'ibyo, ubufasha bwo guhumeka ni ingenzi mu kugabanya ibimenyetso no kurokora ubuzima kandi bushobora kuba bukubiyemo uburyo rusange bwo guhumeka umwuka, umwuka uhagije, umwuka uhumeka utari uhindagurika n'umuyoboro w'umwuka uhumeka bitewe n'uburemere bw'indwara.
Abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bikomeye byo guhumeka bagomba gushyigikirwa na extracorporeal membrane oxygenation (ECMO), uburyo bwo guhindura imikorere y'umutima ukoreshwa mu kuvura umutima cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Byongeye kandi, kubungabunga electrolyte, kwirinda no kuvura ubwandu bwa kabiri hamwe n'ihungabana rya sepsis, no kurinda imikorere y'ingingo z'ingenzi na byo ni ngombwa ku barwayi ba SARS-CoV-2.
Byaramenyekanye ko ibihuha bya sitokine biterwa n'ingaruka z'ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri mu barwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Cytokine ishoramari ni uburyo bw'igisubizo cy'ubuhumekero bw'umubiri bugaragazwa no gukwirakwiza cytokine zirimo TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, na MCP-1.
Iyi cytokine ituma ingirabuzima fatizo z'umubiri zisohora ingano nini y'imikorere mibi y'imikorere mibi, ari nayo mpamvu nyamukuru y'indwara ya ARDS n'imikorere mibi y'ingingo nyinshi.
Immunosuppressants ni ingenzi mu kuvura ibiza bya cytokine, cyane cyane ku barwayi bafite ubukana.
Koroteroide na tocilizumab, anti-IL6 monoclonal antibodies, byakoreshejwe mu kuvura ibiza bya sitokine.
Izindi miti yo kurwanya indwara ziterwa n'imyakura ya sitokine ikubiyemo uburyo bwo guhindura ibisubizo by'umubiri biganisha ku ngirabuzimafatizo za T; kubuza IFN-γ, IL-1, na TNF; kubuza JAK; blinatumomab; kubuza sitokine 4; no kubuza HDAC.
Steroids, nk'imiti igabanya ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, zakoreshejwe cyane mu kuvura SARS mu kugabanya ubukana bw'ibyangiritse mu bwonko.
Nyamara, steroid ku gipimo cyo hejuru ntabwo igira akamaro ku mwuka utera ubumuga bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero mu barwayi ba SARS na COVID-19.
Ku rundi ruhande, steroid ku gipimo cyo hejuru ishobora gutera ingaruka zikomeye, cyane cyane osteonecrosis avascular, bigira ingaruka ku ndwara.
Icyakora, ingano yo hasi kugeza ku gipimo cyo hagati ya corticosteroids mu gihe gito, byasabwe ko ikoreshwa mu buryo bw'ubwitonzi ku barwayi bafite COVID-19 ikomeye.
Mu gihe iyi nkuru yandikwaga, nta miti ya virusi ikora neza yari yemejwe.
Icyakora, gukoresha intravenously na remdesivir, analogue ya nucleotide, byagaragaye ko ari ingirakamaro ku murwayi wo muri Amerika wanduye COVID-19.
Remdesivir ni umuti wa virusi nshya watangijwe na Gilead mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi bwa mbere mu kuvura indwara ziterwa na virusi ya Ebola na Marlburg.
Nyuma, remdesivir yagaragaje ko ishobora no gutera izindi virusi z'umugozi umwe wa RNA harimo virusi ya MERS na SARS.
Ishingiye kuri ibyo, Gilead yahaye uruvange u Bushinwa kugira ngo rukore igerageza ku bantu banduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi ibisubizo byitezwe cyane.
Byongeye kandi, baricitinb, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir, na ribavirin byatanzwe nk'uburyo bushobora kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bukabije.
Diarrhoea, isesemi, gusubiranamo, kwangirika kw'umutima n'ibindi bibazo bishobora kubaho nyuma yo gufata imiti ivanze na lopinavir/ritonavir.
