Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bashobora gukwirakwiza virusi nta bimenyetso bagaragaza mu gihe abarwayi ba SARS bakwirakwiza virusi mu gihe barwaye, bigatuma bigoye kugabanya ubwandu bwa COVID-19 ugereranyije na SARS.
Ibi bisobanuye ko SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwira cyane kandi ku buryo bwihuse kurusha SARS-CoV.
Ibisubizo bya RNA by'ibizamini bya SARS-CoV-2 bishobora kuba bibi ku barwayi ba COVID-19.
Icyakora, abarwayi bakize bashobora kugaragara ko banduye virusi.
Ibi byemezwa n'uko byongera ibyago byo kwandura virusi.
Bitewe n'iterambere rikomeye mu bushakashatsi kuri COVID-19, ibibazo bimwe na bimwe bikenewe bikeneye gukemurwa, birimo:
SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse he?
Nubwo 96% by'abo bantu bahuje ubwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2 na CoV ebyiri nka SARS y'ikinyugunyugu, ntidushobora kwemeza ko SARS-CoV-2 na yo ikomoka ku gikinyugunyugu.
Ese inyamaswa ni zo zinyuranye cyane mu buryo butandukanye zishobora gukwirakwiza virusi zivuye mu ngo, nk'imbeba, zijya ku bantu?
Iyo tutazi igisubizo cya mbere n'icya kabiri, ntidushobora kumenya neza uko icyorezo cyandura, kandi icyorezo gishobora kongera kugaruka igihe icyo ari cyo cyose.
Nubwo igerageza ry'imiterere ya molekile na biochimiya ryagaragaje ko SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano na ACE2, ni gute virusi ishobora kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'umwuka bigatuma habaho impinduka mu maraso?
Ese iyi virusi ishobora no kwinjiza ACE2 mu zindi ngingo?
Nta bisubizo byumvikana kuri ibi bibazo, ntidushobora kugera ku bipimo bya vuba kandi byuzuye ndetse no ku miti myiza.
Iki cyorezo kizakomeza kubaho igihe kingana iki?
Ni gute iyi virusi ikwirakwira mu buryo bw'imiterere binyuze mu kwanduzanya mu bantu?
Ese izaba icyorezo ku isi, ihinduke SARS cyangwa izajya ivuka ukundi nk'ibicurane?
Ibi ni ingenzi ariko bizatwara igihe kugirango tubone ibisubizo by'ibi bibazo hamwe nibindi byinshi.
Ariko kandi, uko ibyo bizatwara amafaranga byaba biri kose, nta kundi twabigenza uretse guhagarika iki cyorezo vuba na bwangu no gusubiza ubuzima bwacu mu buryo busanzwe.
Inkomoko ya zoonotic ya coronavirus y'umuntu
Guhinduka no guhuza n'ibindi byatumye koronavirusi (CoV) n'izindi nyamaswa zayo zikomeye, harimo n'abantu, zihorana ihinduka mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi.
Mbere ya 2003, abantu babiri banduye virusi itera sida (HCoV) bari bazwiho gutera indwara z'ubwoko bworoheje, urugero nk'ibicurane.
Icyorezo cya SARS na MERS byahinduye imyumvire, byerekana ukuntu HCoVs zifite ubukana kandi zishobora guhitana ubuzima.
SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye mu Bushinwa mu mpera za 2019 yatumye abantu benshi bibaza kuri CoV kandi idutangaza kubera ubwandu bworoshye ariko budafite ubwandu bwinshi ugereranyije na SARS-CoV.
Indwara ya HCoV ni zoonosis kandi gusobanukirwa inkomoko ya zoonotic ya HCoV biradufasha.
HCoVs nyinshi zituruka ku birura bitagira ubwandu.
Hari kandi n'izindi HCoVs zizwiho kuba ari inzobere mu kubika virusi.
Kumenya imyanda y'inyamaswa bifite ingaruka ku burinzi bw'indwara z'abantu.
Ubushakashatsi ku mikoranire y'abanduye CoV mu nyamaswa bwatumye haboneka ibisobanuro by'ingenzi ku ndwara ziterwa na CoV mu bantu.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twerekanye isesengura ry'ubumenyi buriho ku barwayi barindwi ba HCoV, twibanda ku mateka y'ubushakashatsi bwabo n'inkomoko ya zoonotic n'ubwandu bw'amoko.
Icy'ingenzi, turagereranya kandi dutandukanya itandukaniro rya HCoVs duhereye ku miterere y'ihindagurika rya virusi no kongera guhuza genome.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 kivugwa muri iyi nkuru.
Byongeye kandi, hakomeje kuvugwa ko hakenewe guhanahana abarwayi neza ndetse n'ingaruka z'ihindagurika rya virusi ku burwayi.
Koronavirusi (CoV) ni zo mu muryango wa Coronaviridae, ugizwe n'itsinda ry'ubwoko bumwe bw'indwara z'agakoko ka RNA, ziteye utwatsi, ziteye mu buryo bw'isura.
Iyi genome iri hagati ya kilobases 26 na 32 mu burebure kandi ni yo genome nini cyane muri virusi za RNA kandi yitwa "CoV" kubera imiterere yayo ya morphologi igaragara nk'ikamba munsi ya mikorosikopi ya elegitoroniki.
Mu byerekeye imiterere, CoV zifite genomes zidafite ibice bitandukanye zisanzwe zifite imiterere imwe.
Bivugwa ko bibiri bya gatatu by'iyi genome bifite ibipimo bibiri binini by'ibisobanuro byuguruye (ORF1a na ORF1b) bihuza, nyuma bigahindurwa pp1a na pp1ab polyprotein replicase.
Izi poroteyine z'amoko menshi zikorwa mu buryo bw'imikorere kugira ngo zitange poroteyine 16 zitagira imiterere, zizwi nka nsp1~16.
Ibisigaye bya genom bigizwe na ORFs ku maporoteyine agizwe n'ibinyabuzima, harimo ipamba (S), isakaro (E), uruhu (M) na nucleoprotein (N).
Poroteyine zimwe na zimwe z'inyongera z'imikorere ya virusi zimwe na zimwe na zo zanditseho imikorere ya virusi zitandukanye.
Bitewe n'itandukaniro ry'urutonde rwa poroteyine, CoVs zigizwe n'imiryango ine (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV na delta-CoV), aho beta-Cov igizwe na HCoVs nyinshi kandi igabanyijemo miryango ine (A, B, C na D).
Ibihamya bya phylogenetic byerekana ko udusimba n'imbeba ari byo bitanga ibinyabuzima byinshi bya alpha-CoV na beta-CoV, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zitanga ibinyabuzima byinshi bya gamma-CoV na delta-CoV.
Mu myaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, CoVs zatsinze inzitizi z'ubwoko bwinshi, ndetse zimwe muri zo zageze aho zigaragara nk'indwara zikomeye ku bantu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana koronavirusi zirindwi z'ubwoko bwa muntu (HCoV).
Muri izo harimo HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 ari na zo alfa-CoVs.
Izindi beta-CoV eshanu ni HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye cyane (SARS-CoV), indwara y'ubuhumekero bwo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS-CoV) na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 akenshi zitera ibimenyetso byoroheje, nk'ibicurane na/cyangwa umubyibuho ukabije.
Ku rundi ruhande, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 nshya zashyizwe ahagaragara ni indwara zandura cyane, zitera indwara zikomeye zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hasi mu barwayi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara y'ubuhumekero (ARDS) n'ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E, B814, bwigaragaje mu myuzure y'abantu barwaye ibicurane mu myaka ya za 1960.
Kuva icyo gihe, ubumenyi bwinshi bwakozwe binyuze mu bushakashatsi bwimbitse kuri HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, byombi bitera ibimenyetso byo kwigenga.
Iki gitekerezo cyakiriwe cyane ko ubwandu bwa HCoV nta cyo bwari buvuze kugeza aho SARS itangiriye.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyabaye mu 2003 kandi ni kimwe mu byorezo byangiza cyane mu mateka, cyanduza abantu barenga 8,000 hamwe n'umubare w'abapfa ungana na 10%.
Nyuma y'imyaka icumi, icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS) cyatumye haba icyorezo gikomeje mu Karere ka Arabiya ndetse n'ibindi byorezo byatangiye gukwirakwira hirya no hino ku isi.
Novel HCoV 2019 (2019-nCoV), yaje kwitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni yo ntandaro y'icyorezo gikomeje cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus ya 2010 (COVID-1), kimaze guhitana ubuzima bw'abantu barenga 3,120 no kwandura abantu barenga 91,000 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Hari imiburo yatanzwe kandi isi igomba kwitegura guhangana n'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
HCoVs zose uko ari ndwi zifite inkomoko zoonotic mu birura, imbeba n'inyamaswa zo mu ngo.
Ibihamya byinshi bishyigikira inkomoko y'ubwihindurize bwa HCov zose mu birura, aho virusi ihinduka vuba kandi itagira ubwandu ariko igaragaza amoko menshi y'ibinyabuzima.
Icyorezo cya COVID-2019 cyazanye ibibazo bikomeye mu buvuzi, siyansi, imibereho myiza n'imyitwarire mu Bushinwa no ku isi yose.
Gukurikirana inkomoko ya zoonotic ya HCoV bitanga urufatiro rwo gusobanukirwa amateka y'ibinyabuzima, imbaraga zitera n'ibikumira isimbuka ry'ubwoko.
Ibi kandi bishobora kuyobora no koroshya gushakisha inyamaswa z'abashyitsi, abahuza n'abateza SARS-CoV-2, bifite ibisobanuro by'ingenzi mu gukumira imvubura mu gihe kizaza.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twerekanye uko imikoranire y'abantu n'inyamaswa, ubwandu bw'ubwoko n'imiterere ya HCoVs byatangiye.
By'umwihariko, twasobanuye kandi tuganira ku nsanganyamatsiko rusange aho virusi ya HCoV idashobora gutera indwara mu bubiko bwa kamere bw'umushyitsi ariko ikaza gutera indwara nyuma yo kwanduzanya mu bwoko bushya.
Nanone kandi, twasuzumye aho HCoVs zagiye zihinduka, aho ubwandu bwagendaga bwiyongera, akenshi bukaba bwari buherekejwe no kugabanuka kw'ubwandu.
Ingaruka z'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 gikomeje na cyo kiravugwa muri iyi nkuru.
Imibiri y'inyamaswa ifite virusi itera sida, yamenyekanye kuva mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 30.
Mbere yo gutandukanya bwa mbere HCoV-229E ubwoko B814 mu mavuta y'izuru y'abarwayi ba influenza, CoV zitandukanye zari zaratandukanyijwe mu matungo atandukanye yanduye, harimo inkoko, imbeba, inka, ingurube, injangwe n'imbwa.
Mu myaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo ishize, HCoVs zirindwi zagiye zishyirwa ahagaragara.
Ibisobanuro byimbitse byamateka y'ubushakashatsi bwa HCoV mu buryo bw'igihe (Imbonerahamwe ya 1) bishobora gutanga amakuru n'inyigisho.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E bwavumbuwe mu nzira y'ubuhumekero bw'abarwayi barwaye indwara y'ubwandu bw'agakoko mu nzira y'ubuhumekero yo hejuru mu 1966, hanyuma buhinduka mu buryo bwo gukura mu nkingi z'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibihaha WI-38.
Abarwayi banduye HCoV-229E bagaragaye bafite ibimenyetso by'ibicurane, birimo umutwe, gusinzira, guhinda umushyitsi no kuribwa mu muhogo, hamwe n'umuriro n'umuhogo bigaragara mu bantu 10~20%.
Nyuma mu 1967, HCoV-OC43 yavuye mu mibiri y'ingingo hanyuma itangira gukwirakwira mu bwonko bw'imbeba.
Isura y'uburwayi bwa HCoV-OC43 igaragara nk'isa n'iy'ubwandu bwa HCoV-229E, mu bimenyetso ntibishobora gutandukanywa n'ubwandu bw'izindi ndwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero nka virusi ya influenza A na rhinovirus.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 byombi byogeye ku isi hose kandi biragaragara ko byandura cyane mu gihe cy'itumba mu turere dufite ikirere gifite ubukonje.
Ubusanzwe, igihe cyo kwinjiza izo virusi zombi ni munsi y'icyumweru, gikurikirwa n'indwara imara ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu bitanze, abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza banduye HCoV-229E barwaye ibicurane byoroheje.
Gusa hari abarwayi bake bafite ubumuga bagaragaza ubwandu bukomeye bw'umuyoboro wo hasi w'ubuhumekero.
SARS, izwi kandi nka atypical pneumonia, ni icyorezo cyatewe na HCoV ya mbere yanditswe neza mu mateka y'abantu kandi umutera wa etiology ni SARS-CoV, HCoV ya gatatu yavumbuwe.
Umuntu wa mbere w'indwara ya SARS ashobora kuboneka mu mpera za 2002 mu Ntara ya Guangdong mu Bushinwa.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyateje ubwandu 8,096 bw'abantu 774 bahitanywe na cyo, mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane myinshi.
Uretse kuba ari super-mupfa, bivugwa ko buri murwayi ashobora gutera abantu babiri ba kabiri, bafite igihe cyo kwibukwa kiri hagati y'iminsi 4 na 7 kandi ko umusemburo utarangwa na virusi ugaragara ku munsi wa 10 w'uburwayi.
Abarwayi banduye SARS-CoV bagaragaza mu ntangiriro uburwayi bw'imitsi, umutwe, umuriro, iseseme n'imbeho, bikurikirwa no kubura umwuka, inkorora n'ubuhumekero budafite ibimenyetso.
Lymphopenia, ibizamini by'imikorere y'umwijima bikwirakwira hamwe n'ubwiyongere bwa creatine kinase ni ibintu bisanzwe mu byumba bya SARS.
Ibyangiritse by'amavomo, kwongera ingirabuzima fatizo z'urukoba no kongera imikorere y'amavomo nabyo byagaragariye mu barwayi ba SARS.
Abagera kuri 20-30% by'abarwayi nyuma yaho bakenera kwitabwaho cyane no guhumeka.
Usibye ubwandu bw'imiyoboro y'ubuhumekero yo hasi, ingingo zitandukanye zirimo imiyoboro y'amaraso, impyiko n'impyiko na zo zishobora kwandura muri ibi bihe bikomeye, akenshi biherekejwe n'umuyaga wa sitokine, ushobora guhitana cyane cyane mu barwayi batagira ubwirinzi.
Virusi yatangiriye mu cyuma cy'ubuhumekero cyafashwe n'umuvandimwe w'umurwayi wafashwe n'icyorezo wari ugiye muri Hong Kong avuye i Guangzhou.
Kuva icyo gihe, hakozwe ubushakashatsi bwinshi kuri HCoV.
HCoV-NL63 yari yarihishe mu mwana w'amezi 7 wo mu Buholandi mu mpera za 2004.
Mu mizo ya mbere, iyi virusi yagaragaye ko ikwirakwira cyane mu bana, abasaza n'abarwayi bafite ubumuga bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
Kurwara indwara y'uruhu, uburwayi bw'amahembe, umuriro n'imyanda y'amaraso ni ibintu bisanzwe mu ndwara ziterwa na HCoV-NL63.
Ubundi bushakashatsi bwigenga bwagaragaje ko virusi nk'iyo yabonetse mu cyuma cy'umunwa w'umwana w'amezi 8 urwaye indwara y'ibihaha mu Buholandi.
Nubwo byamenyekanye mu Buholandi, virusi mu by'ukuri yageze ku isi yose.
Bivugwa ko HCoV-NL63 ari yo ituma abantu benshi barwara indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, kandi ko indwara z'ubuhumekero zikunze kwiyongera mu mpeshyi, mu itumba no mu itumba.
HCoV-NL63 ifitanye isano na laryngite y'ubuhumekero, izwi kandi nka croup.
Muri uwo mwaka, HCoV-HKU1 yari yavanywe mu mugabo w'imyaka 71 wari waragiye mu bitaro arwaye ibicurane n'imyanda y'amaraso muri Hong Kong.
Uretse indwara z'ibicurane n'indwara z'amaraso zandura mu baturage, HCoV-HKU1 na yo yagaragaye ifitanye isano n'indwara y'ibicurane.
Kimwe na HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 iboneka ku isi hose, ituma indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero zigabanuka.
