Muri rusange, iyo HCoVs zigejeje ubushobozi bwo gukwirakwira neza no kuguma mu mubiri w'umuntu, ntizikora nabi cyane cyangwa ngo zibe ziteza indwara.
MERS-CoV yatangiriye mu 2012 mu bihaha by'umurwayi w'imyaka 60 urwaye indwara y'ibihaha n'impyiko muri Arabiya Sawudite.
Nubwo abenshi mu barwayi bemejwe n'ikigo baturutse mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, hari abanduye biturutse mu bindi bihugu, ariko rimwe na rimwe bakandura binyuze mu guhura n'abantu ba hafi, baboneka mu bihugu bitandukanye by'i Burayi no muri Tuniziya.
Indi ndwara ya kabiri yabereye muri Koreya y'Epfo mu 2015 hamwe n'ubwandu 186 bwemejwe.
Ibimenyetso by'uburwayi bwa MERS bisa na SARS, byiganjemo indwara y'ibihaha.
Bitandukanye na SARS, abarwayi benshi barwaye MERS na bo barwara indwara y'impyiko zikomeye, kugeza ubu ari zo zonyine zihariye MERS mu ndwara ziterwa na HCoV.
Abarenga 30% by'abarwayi bagaragaza ibimenyetso byo mu maraso, nk'indwara y'umwijima no gusubiranamo.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, abantu barenga 2500 bemejwe n'abashakashatsi mu by'ubushakashatsi bari bamaze kumenyekana, aho umubare w'abapfa ku kigero cya 34.4% ari wo munini, bituma MERS-CoV iba imwe muri virusi zangiza cyane abantu.
Mu kwezi k'Ukuboza hagati kugeza mu mpera za 2019, itsinda ry'abarwayi ba pneumonia bazwiho kwanduzanya na SARS-CoV-2 ryatangiye kugaragara mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu Ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero bwo hasi ikomeje kwaduka iterwa na SARS-CoV-2 nk'icyorezo cy'indwara y'uburwayi bw'abantu ku rwego mpuzamahanga kandi cyitwa COVID-19.
Kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, abantu 90,053 ni bo bamaze kumenyekana ku isi hose, mu gihe impfu z'abarwayi b'ibibembe ari 3.4%.
Mu buryo bwihariye, umubare w'abandura muri Hubei, mu Bushinwa ni 4.2%, mu gihe umubare w'abandura hanze y'akarere ni 1.2%.
SARS-CoV-2 iteza indwara zikomeye z'ubuhumekero nk'iza SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zigaragara nk'umuriro, inkorora na dyspnea.
Indwara y'umwijima na yo iboneka mu barwayi bamwe na bamwe.
Pneumonia ni kimwe mu bimenyetso bikomeye kandi bishobora kwiyongera vuba bigatuma umuntu agira ikibazo cyo guhumeka nabi.
Nubwo SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 zisa cyane kubera ko zigira homologie y'urusobe rwa nucleotide iri hejuru ya 82%, virusi zigira amashami atandukanye ku giti cya phylogenetic.
SARS-CoV-2 isa n'aho idateje indwara cyane ariko ikandura cyane ugereranyije na SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Abantu bafite ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 baramaze kumenyekana kandi bashobora kuba batuma ikwirakwira ku isi hose mu buryo bwihuse.
Kugereranya no gutandukanya SARS-CoV-2 n'izindi HCoV esheshatu byerekana ibintu byinshi bihambaye bahuriyeho n'ibyo batandukaniyeho.
Icya mbere, igihe cyo kwandura n'igihe indwara ya HCoV imara birasa cyane.
Muri ubwo buryo, SARS-CoV-2 ikurikiza imiterere rusange y'izindi HCoV esheshatu.
Icya kabiri, ubukana bw'ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bwari hagati ya SARS-CoV na HCoV enye zabonetse mu baturage (urugero: HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63).
Ku ruhande rumwe, ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bugaragaza ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara mu gihe cy'ubwandu na HCoVs ziboneka mu baturage, harimo no kugira ibimenyetso bidasanzwe, byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso.
Ku rundi ruhande, igice gito cy'abanduye COVID-19 barembye na cyo gishobora kugaragara nk'uko bimeze ku banduye SARS-CoV, nubwo ari ku kigero cyo hasi.
Icya gatatu, ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 na bwo bugaragaza ibimenyetso bishishikaje bya HCoVs ziboneka mu baturage na SARS-CoV.
Ku ruhande rumwe, ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 ni bwo bufite igipimo cyo hejuru cya HCoVs ziboneka mu baturage.
Ku rundi ruhande, biragoye kwemeza niba ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bugabanuka nyuma yo kwanduza abantu nk'uko byagenze kuri SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Amaherezo, kimwe n'izindi HCoV, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugaragara mu bimenyetso by'imyanda.
