Guhindura ibipimo by'ubushakashatsi ku "baregwa" na "baremejwe" kuri COVID-19 birakenewe
Ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryasohoye amabwiriza yihuse yo gusuzuma no kuvura indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (2019-nCoV), kandi aya mabwiriza atanga uburambe mu kurwanya iki cyorezo ku isi.
Nubwo icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ari icyorezo gishya, ubumenyi n'ubumenyi dufite bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro bitewe n'ubushakashatsi buri gukorwa n'ubunararibonye mu buvuzi; bityo rero, uburyo bwo gusesengura no kuvura burakomeza kuvugururwa.
Muri iyi baruwa, twashubije ku bisobanuro byatanzwe ku mabwiriza yacu kandi dutanga ibipimo bishya by'ubushakashatsi ku "by'ikekwaho" na "byemejwe" nk'uko biteganywa n'amabwiriza mashya (Inyandiko ya karindwi) y'ubushakashatsi no kuvura COVID-19 yatanzwe na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Ubushinwa.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, umugera wa coronavirus 2019 (2019-nCoV) watumye habaho icyorezo, ubu cyitwa coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) kandi virusi yiswe coronavirus 2 y'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yatangaje ko COVID-10 ari icyorezo.
Mu kurwanya ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryateguye amabwiriza yihuse yo gutanga inama kandi ayo mabwiriza yasohotse mu bushakashatsi bw'ubuzima bwa gisirikare ku ya 06 Gashyantare 2020.
Iyo nyandiko yakurikiwe n'abantu benshi kuva yasohoka.
Icyakora, menya ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, ubumenyi n'ubumenyi dufite bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro bitewe n'ibyagezweho mu bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubunararibonye mu buvuzi; bityo rero, uburyo bwo gusuzuma no kuvura bugomba guhora buvugururwa.
Urugero, Igitekerezo cy'Igenzura no Kuvura COVID-19 cyatanzwe na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Abaturage y'Ubushinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), hagati ya 16 Mutarama 2020 na 3 Werurwe 2020, cyasohoye amagazeti arindwi hamwe n'ingingo zimwe na zimwe zihindutse.
Ubu amabwiriza yacu arimo gusuzumwa na Zhou et al., batanze inama yoroheje yo gutanga amanota ashingiye ku buhanga bwabo mu buvuzi.
Imihati yabo yongereye ibihamya bishya ku mabwiriza yacu kandi ni ingirakamaro mu kwerekeza ku cyorezo ku isi hose.
Twishimira imihati ikomeye bashyizeho kandi turabashimira.
Icyakora, imihati yabo ikeneye kandi kuvugururwa hakurikijwe amabwiriza mashya y'igenzura no kuvura COVID-19 (Inyigo ya karindwi) n'ubushakashatsi bushya.
Nk'uko byemejwe n'igazeti ya karindwi (3 Werurwe 2020), kwemeza ko umuntu akekwaho ubwandu bisaba guhuza ibintu by'ingenzi mu mateka y'icyorezo n'ibintu bibiri by'ibimenyetso byo mu buvuzi kugira ngo haboneke isesengura ryuzuye, cyangwa bisaba kuzuza ibintu bitatu by'ibimenyetso byo mu buvuzi mu gihe nta mateka y'icyorezo asobanutse:
Amateka y'icyorezo: (1) Amateka y'urugendo cyangwa gutura mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'akarere kawo, cyangwa mu yindi miryango aho abantu banduye COVID-19 batangajwe mu minsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (2) amateka y'abamenyanye n'ubwandu bw'abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2 (binyuze mu gupima neza za nucleic acid); (3) amateka y'abamenyanye n'abarwayi barwaye umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'akarere kawo, cyangwa mu yindi miryango aho COVID-19 yatangajwe mu minsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (4) amateka afitanye isano n'itsinda ry'abantu banduye byemejwe ((> 2 cases with fever and/or respiratory symptoms occurred within a period of 2 weeks in a small area, such as home, office, classroom at school, etc.).
Ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi: (1) umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka; (2) bifite ibimenyetso byerekana ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) imibare y'utugingo duto tw'amaraso igaragaza ko ari isanzwe, yagabanutse, cyangwa umubare w'utugingo tw'amaraso wagabanutse mu ntangiriro.
Gushakisha umuntu wemejwe ko arwaye bigomba gushingira ku muntu ukekwaho ko arwaye indwara runaka cyangwa ibimenyetso bya serolojiya nk'ibi bikurikira: (1) ibizamini bya PCR by'igihe cya nyacyo bigaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ari yo ndwara; (2) ikinyabiziga cyose cya virusi kigaragaza ko ari kimwe n'izindi koronavirusi; (3) igaragaza ko igaragaza ko hari IgM na IgG mu maraso ya SARS-CoV-2 mu isuzuma ry'amaraso; cyangwa se ko IgG mu maraso ya SaRS-CoV-2 yavuye ku mbi ijya ku nziza, cyangwa se ko igaragaza ko hari inyongera y'ibipimo > inshuro 4 mu gihe cyo gukira hejuru y'icyiciro cy'icyorezo.
Dushobora kubona ko ibizamini bya PCR by'igihe nyacyo bya aside ya nucleic mu nzira y'ubuhumekero cyangwa ibipimo by'amaraso byongerewe ku ncuro ya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) n'iya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020).
Kumenya indwara ziterwa n'ibipimo by'amaraso byinjijwe mu cyiciro cya kane (27 Mutarama 2020) n'icya gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020); hanyuma ibimenyetso bya seroloji byinjijwe mu cyiciro cya karindwi.
Ivugurura rishingiye ku gikorwa gikomeje cy'abashakashatsi bashaka ibikoresho byiza byo gupima aside ya nucleic ku buryo bwo guhita bamenya, ndetse n'ibipimo byo mu nzira y'ubuhumekero birimo ibipimo by'amaraso, byongereye iboneka ry'ibipimo bitandukanye, kandi bifasha kuzana ibisubizo byiza by'abanduye umubiri mu bipimo byemejwe.
Byongeye kandi, hari ibimenyetso byinshi bitwibutsa ko tugomba kwitondera abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso cyangwa batagira ibimenyetso.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, imbonerahamwe y'imikorere ya Zhou et al. yagombaga kuvugururwa, kuko bagaragaje abantu badafite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi nk'abafite "ibyago bike".
Sisitemu y'amanota igomba kandi kwemezwa mu bikorwa no mu bushakashatsi bw'ubuvuzi.
Mu gusoza, twizeye ko ibindi bimenyetso bizabaho kandi dusaba abasomyi bacu gutanga ibitekerezo.
Ku bijyanye no gusuzuma "abashinjwa" n'"abemejwe", turasaba ko bakurikiza amabwiriza mashya y'igihugu bakomokamo.
Itsinda ryacu rizongera kandi kuvugurura amabwiriza yacu rimwe na rimwe kugira ngo ritange ubufasha.
Bangladesh yatangaje abantu batanu bashya bishwe na COVID-19, umubare munini w'abamaze gupfa ku munsi
Ejo, Bangladesh yemeje abantu batanu bashya bishwe na COVID-19 kuri uwo munsi.
Iyi ni yo mibare y'abantu bapfuye ku munsi umwe kurusha abandi bose bishwe n'iyi virusi.
Kugeza ejo, Ikigo cya Bangladesh gishinzwe Epidemiology, Control and Research of Diseases (IEDCR) cyatangaje ko umubare w'ubwandu bwamaze kwandura ukubiyemo abantu 114 bari mu bikorwa n'abantu 33 bakize bari mu rugo.
Abantu 17 bapfuye baramaze kumenyekana.
Mu kiganiro cy'amakuru cyanyujijwe kuri interineti, umuyobozi wa IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, yavuze ko abapfuye barimo abagabo bane n'umugore umwe.
Dr Meerjady yavuze ko babiri muri bo bari mu kigero cy'imyaka 60, babiri muri bo bari mu kigero cy'imyaka 51 na 60, naho undi ari mu kigero cy'imyaka 41 na 50.
Yavuze kandi ko aba bombi bakomokaga i Dhaka.
