Yababwiye ko utwo dukingirizo ari ibintu byinshi, bigatuma umubare w'utwo dukingirizo ugabanuka, maze, iyo twamaze kugurishwa, bigatuma tutagira aho tuba, bigatuma barushaho kumva ko tudafite aho tuba.
Coles na Woolworths bafite igitekerezo [cy'uko] niba hari ibintu byinshi ku mashelufu, niba ibicuruzwa nk'utubati tw'isuku n'ibikoresho byo gusukura bishobora [gucuruzwa] kandi bifite umubare, ushobora kugabanya ubwoba", Russell Zimmerman kuri ABC News.
