Umunara w'Umurinzi wo ku wa Kane w'ikinyamakuru NT News, icapye buri munsi i Darwin, wagize impapuro z'inyongera umunani zigenewe gutemwa no gukoreshwa nk'isuku.
Amaduka yabanje kwanga gushyiraho ibihano, nk'uko bivugwa na ABC Australia ku ya 3 Werurwe aho yabonye bavuga ko nta gahunda bafite yo gushyiraho ibihano ku bicuruzwa.
