Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo
Ku wa Gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryashyize icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiriho  icyorezo cyatewe na coronavirus SARS-CoV-2  nk'icyorezo.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo" ryerekeza gusa ku rugero indwara imaze gukwirakwiraho, aho kwerekeza ku buremere bw'icyorezo runaka, OMS yasanze ari ngombwa guhamagarira leta kugira icyo ikora:
Ibihugu byose biracyafite ubushobozi bwo guhindura icyerekezo cy'iki cyorezo.
Iyo ibihugu byashakishije, bikora ibizamini, bikita ku bantu, bikabashyira mu kato, bikagenzura kandi bigashishikariza abaturage babo kugira icyo bakora, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, yavuze ko ari ngombwa.
Dufite impungenge zikomeye ku byerekeye ubwandu n'ubukana ndetse n'uburangare.
Dukurikije uko Dr. Tom Frieden, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurwanya Indwara abivuga, icyo cyorezo "nticyigeze kibaho mbere hose".
Yavuze ko mu magambo yasohowe na CNN muri Gashyantare, "uretse ibicurane, nta zindi virusi zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero zigeze zigaragara kuva zitangira gukwirakwira ku isi hose".
Ghebreyesus na we yavuze ko "nta kindi gihe twigeze tubona icyorezo cyatewe na coronavirus".
Yakomeje agira ati "kandi ntabwo twigeze tubona icyorezo kimwe kigenzurwa icyarimwe".
Iki cyorezo gishya cyakurikiye icyemezo cya OMS cyo muri Mutarama cyo gutangaza icyorezo nk'icyorezo cy'indwara y'uburwayi bw'abantu ku rwego mpuzamahanga.
Umuyobozi w'Ikigo cy'Amerika Gishinzwe Indwara Zandura n'Ibyago, Dr. Anthony Fauci, yavuze ko iby'iki cyorezo "mu magambo make, bizagenda birushaho kuzamba".
Ku wa Kane, Associated Press yatangaje ko hari nibura abantu 126,000 banduye COVID-19 ku isi, bihitana abantu barenga 4,600.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus 201920 ni icyorezo cy'indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), iterwa n'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye ya coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Icyorezo cyamenyekanye i Wuhan, mu Bushinwa, mu Kuboza 2019, gitangazwa nk'Ubuzima Mpuzamahanga bw'Ubuzima ku rwego mpuzamahanga ku ya 30 Mutarama 2020, gitangazwa nk'icyorezo ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1.61 banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, bihitana abagera ku 97.000.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 bamaze gukira.
Imfu z'abarwayi zitezwe kuba 4% mu Bushinwa, mu gihe ku isi hose ziri hagati ya 13.04% muri Algeria na .08% muri New Zealand.
Ibimenyetso bisanzwe birimo umuriro, inkorora no guhumeka nabi.
Ibibazo bishobora guterwa na Pneumonia na Acute Respiratory Distress Syndrome.
Igihe kuva ku isohorwa kugeza ku kugaragaza ibimenyetso ubusanzwe ni iminsi itanu, ariko bishobora kuba hagati y'iminsi ibiri na cumi n'ine.
Nta rukingo cyangwa imiti yihariye yo kurwanya virusi izwi.
Uburyo bw'ibanze bwo kuvurwa ni uburyo bwo kuvura ibimenyetso no kubishyigikira. Ingamba zo kwirinda zasabwe zirimo gukaraba intoki, gupfuka umunwa mu gihe ukoroye, gukomeza gutandukanya n'abandi, no kugenzura no kwihererana ku bantu bakeka ko banduye.
Abategetsi ku isi hose bitabiriye ibi bikorwa bashyiraho amategeko yo guhagarika ingendo, guhagarika abantu, gufunga abantu, kugenzura akaga ku kazi no gufunga ibigo.
Iki cyorezo cyateje ihungabana ry'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage ku isi, gusubika cyangwa guhagarika ibikorwa by'imikino, amadini, politiki n'umuco, ndetse n'ibura ry'ibicuruzwa byatewe no kugura ibintu mu buryo butunguranye.
Amashuri na za kaminuza byafunzwe haba ku rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa ku rwego rw'akarere mu bihugu 193, bigira ingaruka ku kigero cya 99.4 ku ijana by'abanyeshuri bo ku isi.
Amakuru atari yo kuri iyi virusi yakwirakwijwe kuri interineti, kandi habayeho ibikorwa by'ivangura n'ivangura ku Bashinwa, abandi bantu bakomoka mu Burasirazuba no mu Majyepfo y'Uburasirazuba bw'Aziya n'aho bakomoka, ndetse n'abo mu duce dufite ubwandu bwinshi bwa virusi.
Kubera kugabanya ingendo no gufunga inganda zikomeye, habayeho kugabanuka kw'ibyuka bihumanya ikirere ndetse no kugabanya imyuka ihumanya ikirere.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu Bushinwa (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei) bwavuze ko hari itsinda ry'abantu barwaye indwara y'ibicurane biturutse ku mpamvu zitazwi ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, kandi iperereza ryatangijwe mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020.
Abenshi mu barwayi bafashwe bafitanye isano n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Huanan, kandi bivugwa ko virusi yavuye mu nyamaswa.
Virusi yateje iki cyorezo yitwa SARS-CoV-2, virusi ivumbuwe vuba ifitanye isano ya bugufi na coronavirus y'ikivumbi, coronavirus y'ikinyugunyugu, na SARS-CoV. Umuntu wa mbere uzwiho kugaragaza ibimenyetso yaje kugaragara ko yarwaye ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, kandi uwo muntu nta sano bigaragara yari afitanye na cluster y'amasoko y'amazi yakurikiyeho.
Mu itsinda ry'abanduye batangiye gutangazwa mu Ukuboza 2019, bibiri bya gatatu byabonetse ko bifitanye isano n'isoko.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, raporo idasobanutse yo muri South China Morning Post yagaragaje ko umuntu wari waranduye, yongeye kugaragara ku ya 17 Ugushyingo 2019, mu murwayi w'imyaka 55 wo mu ntara ya Hubei, ashobora kuba ari we wa mbere. Ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko, mu gihe abarwayi bashya bavugwa mu Bushinwa ariko bakiyongera mu buryo butunguranye mu Butaliyani, Irani na Koreya y'Epfo, umubare w'abarwayi bashya hanze y'Ubushinwa warenze umubare w'abarwayi bashya mu Bushinwa ku nshuro ya mbere.
Hashobora kuba hari umubare w'abantu batavuzwe, cyane cyane mu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Kugeza ku ya 26 Gashyantare, hari umubare muto w'abanduye banditswe mu rubyiruko, aho abari bafite imyaka 19 n'abari munsi yayo bangana na 2.4% by'abanduye ku isi. Umujyanama mukuru wa siyansi w'Ubwongereza, Patrick Vallance, yagaragaje ko 60% by'abatuye Ubwongereza bagomba kwandura mbere y'uko ubwirinzi bw'itsinda rikora bushobora kugerwaho.
Umubare w'abanduye ni umubare w'abantu bapimwe bagasanga barwaye COVID-19, kandi bagaragayeho ibimenyetso by'uko banduye nk'uko amategeko abiteganya.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyigeze kigerageza abaturage bacyo barenga 3%, kandi ibihugu byinshi bifite politiki zemewe yo kudapima abantu bagaragaza ibimenyetso byoroheje gusa, nk'u Butaliyani, u Buholandi, Esipanye n'u Busuwisi.
Ubushakashatsi bwanditswe ku ya 16 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku ya 23 Mutarama, abagera kuri 86% by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bataraboneka, kandi ko ubwandu butanditswe ari bwo bwatumye haboneka 79% by'abanduye.
Isesengura ry'ibarurishamibare ryasohotse ku ya 30 Werurwe ryatangajwe ko umubare w'ubwandu mu Butaliyani urenze cyane umubare w'abamaze kwandura.
Igitekerezo cya mbere cy'umubare w'izamuka (R0) kuri COVID-19 ni 1.4 kugeza 2.4.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, bwagaragaje ko uwo mubare ushobora kuba 5.7.
Abantu benshi banduye COVID-19 barakira.
Ku badafite ibimenyetso, igihe cyo kubaho k'ibimenyetso kugeza ku rupfu kiri hagati y'iminsi 6 na 41, aho ibisanzwe ari iminsi 14.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera ku 97,000 bapfuye bahitanwe na COVID-19.
Mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku ya 5 Gashyantare, hafi 80% by'abapfuye bari mu bantu barengeje imyaka 60, kandi 75% bari bafite ibibazo by'ubuzima biriho harimo indwara z'umutima na diyabete. Umubare w'abapfuye ku bw'icyorezo cya COVID-19 muri rusange werekeza ku bapfuye basuzumwe bagasanga baranduye COVID hakurikijwe amabwiriza yemewe.
Umubare w'abapfuye by'ukuri ba COVID-19 ushobora kuba ari munini cyane, kuko ushobora kuba utarimo abapfuye batapimwe - urugero nko mu ngo, mu bigo byita ku barwayi, n'ibindi.
Amakuru amwe n'amwe aturuka mu Butaliyani agaragaza ko umubare w'abantu bapfuye cyane muri iki cyorezo warenze umubare w'abantu bapfuye bishwe na COVID ku buryo bungana n'incuro 4-5.
Umuvugizi w'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) yagize ati "Turabizi ko [umubare w'abapfuye] ari ugukabya", amagambo ashyigikiwe n'amakuru y'inkuru zivuga ku kubura umubare muri Amerika.
Urupfu rwa mbere hanze y'u Bushinwa rwabaye ku ya 1 Gashyantare muri Filipine, naho urupfu rwa mbere hanze ya Aziya rwabaye mu Bufaransa ku ya 14 Gashyantare.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, hanze y'u Bushinwa, abantu barenga icumi na babiri bapfuye ku gihugu kimwe baranditswe muri Irani, Koreya y'Epfo n'u Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku ya 13 Werurwe, ibihugu birenga mirongo ine n'uturere byatangaje ko hapfuye abantu, ku migabane yose uretse Antarctica.
Iyi mibare itandukana bitewe n'akarere n'igihe, kandi biganishwa nubwinshi bw'ibizamini, ubwiza bw'ubuzima, amahitamo y'ubuvuzi, igihe kuva icyorezo cyatangira, hamwe nibintu by'abaturage nk'imyaka, igitsina, n'ubuzima rusange.
Dukurikije imibare ya Johns Hopkins University, igipimo cy'urupfu ku barwayi ku isi ni 6.0% (97,039/1,617,204) kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020.
Iyo mibare igenda itandukana bitewe n'akarere.
Mu Bushinwa, imibare y'impfu z'abarwaye yagabanutse iva kuri 17.3% (ku bafite ibimenyetso kuva ku ya 110 Mutarama 2020) igera kuri 0.7% (ku bafite ibimenyetso kuva ku ya 1 Gashyantare 2020).Izindi ngero zirimo igipimo cy'urupfu rw'abarwaye (CFR), kigaragaza igipimo cy'abavumbuwe bapfuye bazize indwara, n'igipimo cy'abapfuye bazize ubwandu (IFR), kigaragaza igipimo cy'abavumbuwe (bavumbuwe n'abataravumbuwe) bapfuye bazize indwara.
Iyi mibare ntabwo ifitanye isano n'igihe kandi ikurikira abaturage runaka kuva ku banduye kugeza ku barwayi.
Hari abanyeshuri bagerageje kubara iyi mibare ku baturage runaka.
Ikigo cya Kaminuza ya Oxford gishinzwe ubuvuzi bushingiye ku bimenyetso, gitanga raporo y'uko umubare w'abandura bapfa kubera icyorezo muri rusange uri hagati ya 0.1% na 0.39%.
Ibipimo byo hejuru by'uru rwego birahuza n'ibyavuye mu igerageza rya mbere rya COVID-19 mu Budage, n'ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bw'ibarurishamibare busesengura ingaruka z'igerageza ku kigereranyo cya CFR.
OMS yemeje ko iki cyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa.
Igihe cy'icyorezo n'igihe cy'ikirere cy'icyorezo ntabwo bizwi kandi bishobora gutandukana bitewe n'ahantu.
Maciej Boni wo muri kaminuza ya Leta ya Pennsylvania yagize ati "Iyo indwara yanduye itagenzuwe, akenshi iba igaragara mu buryo bw'ikirere, hanyuma igatangira gukendera iyo inzu zibuze.
Ariko kandi, ubu biragoye cyane kumenya igihe ibyo bizabera".
Umujyanama mukuru mu by'ubuvuzi wa leta y'Ubushinwa, Zhong Nanshan, yavuze ko "icyorezo gishobora kurangira muri Kamena" mu gihe ibihugu byose byashishikarizwa gukurikiza inama za OMS ku ngamba zo guhagarika ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharski wo mu ishuri ry'isuku n'ubuvuzi bw'ikirere i Londres yavuze ko SARS-CoV-2 "izakomeza gukwirakwira, wenda mu mwaka umwe cyangwa ibiri".
Nk'uko bivugwa n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Neil Ferguson wo muri Imperial College, kugabanya imishyikirano hagati y'abantu n'ibindi bizakenerwa "kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse (hashobora gushira amezi 18 cyangwa arenga)".
William Schaffner wo muri Kaminuza ya Vanderbilt yagize ati "Ntekereza ko coronavirus idashobora guhita ihita ishira burundu kuko yandura cyane" kandi ko "ishobora kuba indwara y'igihe, igaruka buri mwaka".
Ingaruka z'uko bazongera kugaruka zizaba zishingiye ku bushobozi bw'ingurube n'urwego rw'ihindagurika ry'imiterere y'iyo virusi.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidasanzwe kandi abantu banduye bashobora kuba badafite ibimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso bibiri by'ibanze ni umuriro (88%) n'umuhogo ushyushye (68%).
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara harimo umunaniro, kubyara ibibyimba byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero (kudahumeka), kubura impumuro, guhumeka nabi, ububabare bw'umubiri n'ubuhumekero, kubabara mu muhogo, umutwe, imbeho, gusubiranamo, hemoptysis, iseseme cyangwa cyanotic.
Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga ibimenyetso by'ihungabana nk'ububabare bwo guhumeka, kubabara cyangwa guhangayika mu gatuza guhoraho, guhinda umushyitsi, kugorwa no kubyuka, n'amaso cyangwa iminwa guhinduka ubururu; kwihutira kwivuza birasabwa iyo ibi bimenyetso bihari. Kwiyongera kw'indwara bishobora gutuma umuntu arwara imibyimba ikomeye, indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye ubwoba, sepsis, sepsis, septic shock n'urupfu.
Abantu bamwe na bamwe banduye bashobora kuba nta bimenyetso bagaragaza, nta bimenyetso by'uburwayi bafite ariko ibipimo byemeza ko banduye, bityo abashakashatsi batanze inama ko abantu bahuye cyane n'abantu banduye bagombye gukurikiranwa cyane no gusuzumwa kugira ngo barebe ko nta bwandu bafite.
Ubushinwa buvuga ko umubare w'abadafite ibimenyetso uturuka ku bantu bake ugera kuri 44%.
Igihe gisanzwe cyo kugabanya (igihe hagati y'ubwandu n'indwara) kuva ku munsi umwe kugeza ku minsi 14; akenshi ni iminsi itanu. Nk'urugero rw'ibihe bidashidikanywaho, imibare y'abantu barwaye COVID-19 batakaje impumuro yabo mu ntangiriro ya 30% hanyuma igabanuka ikajya kuri 15%.
Hari byinshi bitaramenyekana ku buryo iyi ndwara ikwirakwira.
Iyi ndwara bivugwa ko yandura cyane cyane mu gihe cyo guhura no mu matembabuzi mato aturuka mu gukorora, kwitsamura, cyangwa kuvuga; mu gihe cyo guhura cyane umuntu aba ari ku ntera ya metero 1 kugeza kuri 2 (3 kugeza ku birenge 6).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukorora udakingiye bizatuma udutonyanga twa ai dutambuka metero 4.5 (15 ft) kugeza metero 8.2 (27 ft).
Hari abavuze ko virusi ishobora no kwanduzwa n'udutonyanga duto tumara igihe kirekire mu mwuka, dushobora gutangwa mu gihe cyo kuvuga. Udutonyanga tw'umwuka dushobora no gutangwa mu gihe cyo guhumeka, harimo no mu gihe cyo kuvuga, nubwo virusi muri rusange idaterwa n'umwuka.
Amadosiye ashobora kugwa mu kanwa cyangwa mu mazuru y'abantu bari hafi cyangwa ashobora guhumeka akajya mu bihaha.
Uburyo bumwe na bumwe bwa magendu nka intubation na cardiopulmonary resuscitation (CPR) bushobora gutuma umwanda wo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero uterwa kandi bigatuma habaho gukwirakwiza umwuka.
Virusi ishobora kandi gukwirakwira iyo umuntu akoze ku kintu cyanduye, harimo uruhu, hanyuma agakora ku maso, izuru cyangwa akanwa.
Nubwo hari impungenge ko virusi ishobora gukwirakwira mu binyoma, iki cyorezo nta ngaruka mbi kigira.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yahakanye ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura mu kanwa binyuze mu busabe. Virusi yandura cyane mu minsi itatu ya mbere nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso, ariko ubwandu bushobora kubaho mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bigaragara no mu byiciro by'ubudehe.
Abantu basuzumwe bagasanga barwaye iyo ndwara mbere y'iminsi itatu batangiye kugaragaza ibimenyetso, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko ubwandu bushobora kubaho mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bigaragara.
Raporo nke cyane z'abanduye zemeza ko nta bimenyetso bafite, ariko ubwandu bw'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwemejwe n'ibihugu bimwe na bimwe mu gihe cy'iperereza ryo kumenya abo bantu.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) kivuga ko nubwo bitamenyekanye neza uko byoroshye kwandura, umuntu umwe ubusanzwe yandura abandi bantu babiri cyangwa batatu.
By'umwihariko, virusi yagaragaye ko ishobora kugaragara mu minsi igera kuri itatu kuri plastiki (polypropylene) na 304, ku munsi umwe kuri karito, no mu masaha agera kuri ane ku cyuma.
Ibi ariko, bitandukanye bitewe n'ubushyuhe n'ubushyuhe. Amatungo n'ibindi bikoko byagiye bipimisha COVID-19
Nta gihamya igaragaza ko inyamaswa zishobora kwanduza abantu, ariko abategetsi b'Ubwongereza batanga inama yo gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukora ku nyamaswa, nko gukora ku bindi bintu bishobora kuba byakozwe n'abantu banduye.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ni virusi nshya, yabanje gutandukanywa n'abantu batatu barwaye ibicurane by'imyotsi bifitanye isano n'ihuriro ry'indwara y'ubuhumekero i Wuhan.
Ibintu byose biranga virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 bibaho bijyanye na koronavirusi mu bidukikije. Hanze y'umubiri w'umuntu, virusi yicwa na savoni yo mu rugo, isenya umwambaro wayo urinda. SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano ya hafi na SARS-CoV y'inkomoko.
Bivugwa ko iyi virusi ikomoka ku nyamaswa.
Isesengura ry'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima ryagaragaje ko koronavirusi ari imwe mu bwoko bwa Betacoronavirus, mu bwoko bwa Sarbecovirus (inkomoko ya B) hamwe n'udutsi tubiri twavanywe mu birura.
Iyi virusi ifite ihure rya 96% ku rwego rwa genom yuzuye n'indi koronavirusi y'ikinyugunyugu (BatCov RaTG13).
Muri Gashyantare 2020, abashakashatsi bo mu Bushinwa basanze hari itandukaniro rimwe gusa rya amino acide mu bice runaka bya genomic sequence hagati ya virusi zo mu bwoko bwa thyroid na virusi zo mu bwoko bw'abantu.
Itandukaniro rya jenome yose kugeza ubu ryagaragaje ko 92% by'ibinyabuzima by'ibanze bigabanyijemo coronavirus ya shingles na SARS-CoV-2, ibyo bikaba bidahagije kugira ngo bigaragaze ko shingles ari indangamuntu yo hagati.
Indwara y'iyo virusi ishobora kwemezwa by'agateganyo hakurikijwe ibimenyetso, nubwo amaherezo byemezwa binyuze mu guhindura inyandiko y'ibisubizo bya polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) y'imyanda yanduye cyangwa kwifotoza kuri CT.
Ubushakashatsi bwagereranyije PCR na CT i Wuhan bwemeje ko CT irusha cyane kumva PCR, nubwo idasanzwe, aho ibyinshi mu bimenyetso byayo bibangikanye n'imiterere ya pneumonia n'izindi ndwara.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika cy'Ubumenyi mu by'Imiyoboro ya Radiyo cyatangaje ko "CT itagomba gukoreshwa mu gupima cyangwa nk'ikigo cya mbere cyo gupima COVID-19".
OMS yasohoye ibyangombwa byinshi byo gupima RNA bya SARS-CoV-1, ibya mbere byatanzwe ku ya 17 Mutarama.
Ibizamini bikoresha uburyo bwo gusubiza mu buryo bwa polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) mu gihe nyacyo.
Ibi bizageragezwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero cyangwa amaraso.
Ibisubizo by'ibizamini ubusanzwe biboneka mu masaha make kugeza ku minsi mike.
Ubusanzwe ibi bipimo bikorwa hakoreshejwe ibipimo bya nasopharyngeal ariko ibipimo bya cornea nabyo birashobora gukoreshwa.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, nta na kimwe muri ibi bipimo cyagaragaye ko gihagije ku buryo cyemewe gukoreshwa cyane.
Muri Amerika, ibizamini bya seroloji byakozwe na Cellex byemejwe ko bikoreshwa mu buryo bw'impanuka n'ibigo byemewe gusa.
Ibimenyetso by'amashusho kuri radiograph na tomographie (CT) by'imbeba z'indwara zirimo isura y'ibirahuri by'ubutaka bidasa n'ibisanzwe n'ibura ry'imyanda.
Ishyirahamwe ry'abashakashatsi mu by'imashini zo mu Butaliyani ririmo riteranya ibipimo byo ku mbuga za interineti kugira ngo rishake amashusho y'abanduye.
Kubera guhura n'izindi ndwara nka adenovirus, gufata amashusho nta kwemeza na PCR bifite umwihariko uciriritse mu kumenya COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeye bwakozwe mu Bushinwa bwagereranyije ibisubizo bya CT y'agafu na PCR kandi bwerekana ko nubwo amashusho adashyize mu gaciro ku banduye, uburyo bwihuse kandi bwumvisha, bugatanga igitekerezo cyo gusuzuma uburyo nk'igikoresho cyo gupima mu turere turimo icyorezo.
Urusobe rw'imitsi y'uruziga ishingiye ku bwenge bw'ubuhinga bw'ikoranabuhanga rwakozwe kugira ngo rufate ibipimo bya virusi kuri radiyo na CT.
Uburyo bwo kwirinda kwandura indwara harimo kugira isuku rusange, gukaraba intoki, kwirinda gukora ku maso, izuru cyangwa umunwa udakaravye, no gukorora cyangwa gusinzira ku kintu hanyuma ukacyura mu myanda.
Abashobora kuba baranduye basabwe kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu ruhame.
Ingamba zo kwirinda abantu ku mubiri na zo zatangajwe mu rwego rwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo.
Nyamara, virusi imaze kugera ku rwego rwo gukwirakwira mu baturage mu bice byinshi by'isi.
Ibi bivuze ko virusi ikwirakwira mu baturage, kandi bamwe mu baturage ntibazi aho banduye cyangwa uko banduye. Abashinzwe ubuzima bita ku muntu ushobora kwandura barasabwa gukoresha ingamba zisanzwe zo kwirinda, ingamba zo kwirinda guhura, no kurinda amaso. Kurasa no guhura ni uburyo bwingenzi bwo kumenya isoko y'ubwandu no kwirinda kwanduzanya.
Gukoresha amakuru y'aho umuntu ari kuri telefoni zigendanwa na leta kuri iyi mpamvu byateje impungenge ku byerekeye ubuzima bwite, aho Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe arenga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko hakorwa ingamba zo kugabanya ubwo buyobozi.
Porogaramu zitandukanye za mobile zashyizwe mu bikorwa cyangwa zashyizweho ku bushake, kandi kugeza ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'inzobere arenga icumi arimo gukora ku bisubizo bishimangira ubuzima bwite, nk'ikoreshwa rya Bluetooth mu kwandikisha hafi y'umukoresha kuri telefoni ye igendanwa.
Abakoresha nyuma babona ubutumwa niba baragiranye imishyikirano ya bugufi n'umuntu wafashwe na COVID-19. Ibinyoma birimo gukwirakwira ku buryo bwo kwirinda ubwandu; kuruka amazuru no gukorora umuti w'ibinyobwa, urugero, ntibikora.
Nta rukingo rwa COVID-19 ruriho, nubwo imiryango myinshi irimo gukora cyane.
Gukaraba intoki ni ingenzi mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo.
CDC itera inkunga abaturage gukaraba intoki kenshi bakoresheje isabune n'amazi mu gihe cy'amasegonda nibura makumyabiri, cyane cyane nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero cyangwa igihe intoki zigaragara zanduye; mbere yo kurya; no nyuma yo guhekenya, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Ibyo biterwa n'uko iyo virusi ivuye mu mubiri w'umuntu, yica isabune yo mu rugo, ikangiza udukingirizo.
CDC ikomeza itera inkunga gukoresha imiti yo gukaraba intoki ikoreshwa n'inzoga irimo nibura 60% by'inzoga iyo isabune n'amazi bidahari.
OMS igira inama abaturage kwirinda gukora ku maso, amazuru cyangwa umunwa batabanje gukaraba intoki.
Urusobe rushobora kwandura hamwe na serivisi (mu munota umwe wo kwanduzwa na disinfectant ku gice cy'ibyuma bitagira ingeso), harimo 6271% ya ethanol, 50100% ya isopropanol, 0.1% ya sodium hypochlorite, 0.5% ya hydrogen peroxide, na 0.27.5% ya povidone-iodine.
Ibindi bikoresho, nka benzalkonium chloride na chryoxydine gluconate, ntabwo bikora cyane.
CDC itera inkunga ko mu gihe hari umuntu ukekwaho cyangwa wemejwe ko yanduye COVID mu bigo nk'ibiro cyangwa ibigo byita ku bana, ahantu hose nko mu biro, mu bwiherero, ahantu rusange, ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bifatika nk'amatabuleti, imashini zikora ku gikoresho cy'ikoranabuhanga, imashini zikoresha ifoni, ibikoresho byo kugenzura kure n'imashini za ATM zikoreshwa n'abantu barwaye, bigomba kugezwa mu kato.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuzima asaba abantu gupfuka umunwa n'amazuru yabo n'amaboko yabo cyangwa utuntu mu gihe bakoroye cyangwa batutse, no guhita batakaza utwo dukoresho.
Ibirinda kurwara by'ubuvuzi birasabwa ku bantu bashobora kwandura, kuko kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya umubare n'intera y'amaraso y'umwuka w'umwuka wanduye mu gihe uvuga, unyenyera, cyangwa ukoroye.
OMS yashyizeho amabwiriza ku gihe n'uburyo bwo kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Stephen Griffin, impuguke mu by'ubwandu bw'indwara muri Kaminuza ya Leeds, yagize ati "Kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya abantu guhora bakora ku maso, ari na byo bitera ubwandu cyane cyane mu gihe badafite isuku y'intoki".
OMS yasabye abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza kwambara udupfukamunwa gusa mu gihe bafite ibyago byinshi, nk'abita ku bantu barwaye COVID-19, nubwo yemera ko kwambara udupfukamunwa bishobora gufasha abantu kwirinda gukorakora mu maso.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byatangiye gushishikariza abaturage kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, CDC itera inkunga ikoreshwa ry'udupfukamunwa tudafite ubumara (non-medical face masks) dukorwa mu myenda. Ubushinwa bwatanze inama ku buryo bwihariye yo gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'impuha tw'ubwoko bumwe n'ubundi ku bantu bafite ubuzima bwiza, cyane cyane iyo bari mu mishyikirano ya hafi (metero 1 (3 ft) cyangwa munsi yayo) n'abandi bantu.
Hong Kong irasaba kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe ukoresha imodoka cyangwa ahantu hari abantu benshi.
Abashinzwe ubuzima muri Thailand bashishikariza abantu gukora udupfukamunwa tw'impu mu ngo zabo no kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza gukaraba buri munsi.
Repubulika ya Tchèque na Slovakiya bibuza abantu kujya mu ruhame batambaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa ngo bapfuke umunwa n'amazuru.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Vietnam yasabye abantu bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bagiye ahantu hahurira abantu benshi kugira ngo birinde n'abandi.
Leta ya Autriche yategetse ko abantu bose binjira mu maduka y'ubucuruzi bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Israel yasabye abaturage bayo bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu ruhame.
Taiwan, imaze gukora udupfukamunwa miliyoni icumi buri munsi kuva mu kwezi kwa gatatu, yasabye abagenzi bo mu mihanda ya gari ya moshi n'amabisi yo hagati mu mijyi kwambara udupfukamunwa kuva ku ya 1 Mata.
Panama yasabye abantu kwambara udupfukamunwa igihe bari hanze, ndetse itera inkunga abantu batishoboye gukora udupfukamunwa mu ngo zabo.
Udupfukamunwa tw'amaso kandi twakoreshejwe cyane mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Malaysia na Singapore.
Gufunga abantu (nanone byitwa gufunga ku mubiri) bijyana n'ibikorwa byo kugenzura ubwandu bigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara mu kugabanya guhura cyane kw'abantu.
Ingamba zirimo guhagarika abantu; guhagarika ingendo; no gufunga amashuri, ahantu ho gukorera, ibibuga by'imikino, za sitade cyangwa ibigo by'ubucuruzi.
Abantu bashobora gushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo kwitarura abandi mu kuguma mu ngo zabo, kugabanya ingendo, kwirinda ahantu hari abantu benshi, gukoresha indamutso zidakora, no kwitandukanya n'abandi.
Ubu leta nyinshi zisaba cyangwa zisaba abantu kujya mu kato mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Umubare w'abantu benshi bateranira hamwe, nk'uko byemejwe n'inzego za Leta z'Amerika n'imiryango y'ubuzima, wagabanyijwe vuba kuva ku bantu 250 (niba nta bwandu bwa COVID-19 buzwi muri ako karere) ukagera ku bantu 50, hanyuma ukagera ku bantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwashyizeho itegeko ribuza guteranira hamwe kw'abantu barenze babiri. Abasaza n'abafite ibibazo by'ubuzima bihishwe nk'indwara ya diyabete, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko ukabije w'amaraso, n'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya indwara zangiza umubiri, bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zikomeye n'ibibazo kandi CDC yabasabye kuguma mu rugo uko bishoboka kose mu duce dufite icyorezo cy'abaturage. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, OMS n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima zatangiye gusimbuza ikoreshwa ry'ijambo "gufunga abantu" "gufunga mu buryo bw'umubiri", bisobanurwa ko intego ari ukugabanya guhuza umubiri mu gihe ukomeza imishyikirano y'abantu, haba kuri interineti cyangwa kure.
Gukoresha ijambo "gufunga abantu" byateje impamvu ko abantu bagomba kubaho mu bwigunge rusange, aho kubatera inkunga yo gushyikirana n'abandi binyuze mu bundi buryo.
Muri ibyo harimo no kugusaba kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina n'umuntu ubana nawe gusa, udafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso bya virusi.
Abantu bagaragaweho COVID-19 n'abakekwaho kuyandura, basabwe kuguma mu kato.
Ibigo by'ubuzima byatanze amabwiriza arambuye ku bijyanye no kwitarura abantu mu buryo bukwiriye. Leta nyinshi zategetse cyangwa zasabye ko abaturage bose batuye mu duce twatewe n'icyorezo bashyirwa mu kato.
Amabwiriza akomeye cyane yo kwisanzura yashyizwe ku bantu bari mu matsinda afite ibyago byinshi.
Abantu bashobora kuba baragaragaye ku muntu ufite COVID-19 n'ababa barigeze gutembera mu bihugu cyangwa uturere dufite ubwandu bwagutse bagiriwe inama yo kwiherera mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 uhereye igihe bashoboraga kuheruka kubigaragariza.
Uburyo bwo kugabanya icyorezo ni uguhagarika cyangwa kugabanya.
Gufunga bikorwa mu bihe bya mbere by'icyorezo kandi bigamije gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abanduye no gushyiraho izindi ngamba zo kugenzura ubwandu no gukingira kugira ngo bahagarike indwara ntizigere zikwirakwira mu baturage.
Iyo bitagishoboka guhashya ikwirakwira ry'iyo ndwara, imbaraga zihita zijya mu cyiciro cyo kugabanya: ingamba zifatwa zo kugabanya ikwirakwira no kugabanya ingaruka ku mashyirahamwe y'ubuzima no ku baturage.
Iterambere ry'igihugu rigomba kuba ryarakozwe mu buryo bw'ubushake.
Ibishuko bisaba ingamba zikomeye zo guhagarika icyorezo mu kugabanya umubare w'ababana munsi ya 1. Igice cyo gucunga ikwirakwira ry'indwara zandura ni ugushaka kugabanya icyorezo, kizwi nko guhanagura icyorezo.
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo kuremererwa kw'ubuvuzi kandi bigatanga igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Ibipimo byo kwirinda bidashingiye ku miti bishobora gucunga ubwandu birimo ingamba zo kwirinda bwite, nko kugira isuku y'amaboko, kwambara udupfukamunwa, no kwisanzura; ingamba zigamije abaturage ku isuku y'umubiri nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika amateraniro manini; uruhare rw'abaturage mu gushishikariza abantu kwakira no kwitabira bene izo ngamba; kimwe n'ingamba z'ibidukikije nko gusukura. Ingamba zikomeye cyane zigamije guhashya ubwandu zafashwe mu Bushinwa nyuma y'uko ubukana bw'icyorezo bugaragaye, urugero nko gushyira abantu mu kato mu mijyi yose no gushyiraho amategeko yo kubuza ingendo.
Ibihugu bindi na byo byatangiye gufata ingamba zitandukanye zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho uburyo bukomeye bwo gupima no gushyira abantu mu kato, ndetse itanga n'inkunga ku bimuka by'abantu banduye.
Singapore itanga inkunga y'amafaranga ku banduye bishyira mu kato kandi igafatira ibihano bikomeye abananirwa kubikora.
Taiwan yongereye umusaruro w'udupfukamunwa no guhana ibihano ku bijyanye no guhisha ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi. Imyiteguro yo mu Bwongereza no muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yerekana ko kugabanya (kugabanya ariko ntihagarike ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) no kugabanya (kugabanya ubwiyongere bw'icyorezo) bifite imbogamizi zikomeye.
Politiki nziza yo kugabanya ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abasaba ubuvuzi ku kigero cya 2/3 n'urupfu ku kigero cya kimwe cya kabiri, ariko igatuma abantu ibihumbi amagana bapfa kandi ikongera umutwaro ku ngamba z'ubuzima.
Ingamba zishobora kuba ari amahitamo ariko zigomba gukomeza igihe cyose virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse, niba ari rwo rwabanje), kuko ikwirakwira ryayo rizongera vuba igihe ingamba zo kwirinda zizaba zaragabanyijwe.
Ibiganiro by'igihe kirekire byo guhashya icyorezo bitera ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza.
Nta muti wa virusi wemewe ku buryo bwihariye kuri COVID-19, ariko ibikorwa byo kuwushyira mu bikorwa birakomeje, harimo no gupima imiti iriho.
Kunywa imiti ya farini, amazi meza no kuruhuka bihagije bifasha kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bitewe n'uburemere, imiti ya ogisijeni, uruvange rw'umuyoboro w'amaraso n'ubufasha bwo guhumeka bishobora kuba ngombwa.
Gukoresha za stéroïdes bishobora gutuma ibikomere birushaho kwiyongera.
Hari imiti imwe n'imwe yari yemewe mbere mu kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi iri kugeragezwa mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS kandi yavuze ko hari "uburyo busanzwe n'ubundi bwo kwivuza mu rugo" bushobora koroshya ibimenyetso biterwa na SARS-CoV-19.
Kongera ubushobozi no guhuza ubuvuzi n'ibikenewe n'abarwayi ba COVID-19 byasobanuwe na OMS nk'ingamba z'ibanze zo guhangana n'icyorezo.
ECDC n'ibiro bya WHO byo mu Burayi byatanze amabwiriza ku bitaro n'ibigo by'ubuzima by'ibanze yo kwimura ibikoresho ku rwego rutandukanye, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu ikoranabuhanga mu gupima COVID-19, gukuraho uburyo bwo kwipimisha aho bikenewe, gushyira mu kato no gushyira mu kato abarwayi bafite COVID-19, no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi ba mbere binyuze mu gutoza abakozi no kongera umubare w'imashini zitanga umwuka n'ibitanda.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku byerekeye aho abarwayi ba mbere (bitwa abarwayi batagira umubare) bakomoka.
Umuntu wa mbere uzwiho coronavirus nshya ashobora kuba yarapfuye tariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan, Hubei, Ubushinwa.
Mu kwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wagendaga wiyongera buhoro buhoro.
Ibi byaha byiganjemo ibijyanye n'isoko ry'ibyokurya byo mu nyanja rya Huanan, rikunda kugurisha inyamaswa nzima, kandi igitekerezo kimwe ni uko virusi yavuye muri kimwe muri ibi bikoko; cyangwa, mu yandi magambo, ifite inkomoko ya zoonotic.
Ku ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan bamenyesheje bagenzi babo ko hari "indwara ya coronavirus imeze nka SARS".
Aba baganga umunani, barimo Li Wenliang, bari barahawe umuburo na polisi kubera gukwirakwiza ibihuha by'ibinyoma, undi, Ai Fen, yacyashwe n'abamusumbaga kubera gutera icyo kibazo.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan y'Umujyi yaje gushyiraho itangazo rusange ku ya 31 Ukuboza, imenyesha OMS.
Abantu benshi cyane barwaye indwara y'ibicurane bataramenyekana, batangajwe n'inzego z'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntangiriro za Mutarama kugira ngo hatangizwe iperereza.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze no mu tundi turere tw'Ubushinwa, ifashwa n'impunzi z'umwaka mushya w'Ubushinwa, maze Wuhan ihinduka ikigo cy'ingendo ndetse n'ahantu h'ingenzi hahurira gari ya moshi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwavuze ko bwabonye abarwayi bashya bagera ku 140 ku munsi, barimo babiri i Beijing n'umwe i Shenzhen.
Amakuru yemewe nyuma yagaragaje ko abantu 6,174 bari baragaragaje ibimenyetso ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020.Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yarenze Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani ku mubare munini w'abanduye kw'isi.Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, abasaga miliyoni 1.61 bamaze kumenyekana ku isi hose; abantu barenga 97,000 barapfuye kandi abarenga 364,000 barakize.
Ibihugu n'uturere bigera kuri 200 byamaze kugira nibura umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera iki cyorezo mu Burayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije urujya n'uruza rw'abantu no gushyiraho imipaka.
Igisubizo cy'igihugu cyashyizemo ingamba zo kugabanya abantu nk'igenzurwa (zwi nka amabwiriza yo kuguma mu rugo, amabwiriza y'ubwugamo, cyangwa amabwiriza y'ibihe bidasanzwe) n'amabwiriza yo gufunga.Ku ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300, cyangwa hafi 90% by'abatuye isi, bari mu bihe bidasanzwe muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari mu bihe bidasanzwe muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 59 bari mu bihe bidasanzwe muri Afurika y'Epfo n'abantu miliyari 1.3 bari mu bihe bidasanzwe mu Buhinde.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu bihe bidasanzwe, byazamutse bigera kuri miliyari 2.6 nyuma y'iminsi ibiri - hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko yanduye COVID 19 yongeye kugaragara ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan; raporo idafite gihamya igaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere yanduye ari ku ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Umuganga Zhang Jixiang yabonye itsinda ry'abantu barwaye indwara y'ibicurane ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, nyuma ibitaro bye byamenyesheje CDC ya Wuhan Jianghan ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ibizamini bya mbere bya jenoside ku bipimo by'abarwayi ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 byerekanye ko coronavirus nk'iya SARS iriho.
Itangazo rusange ryatanzwe na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza.
WHO yabimenyeshejwe uwo munsi.
Mu gihe iyi nkuru yari ikiri kuvugwa, abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan bari barahawe umuburo n'igipolisi kubera "gukwirakwiza ibihuha" ku cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta "gihamya ihamye" y'ubwandu bw'abantu ku bantu.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bukabije bwaje kuvugwa n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa Xi Jinping nk'"intambara y'abaturage" yo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Mu cyiswe "igikorwa gikomeye cyane cyo gushyira abantu mu kato mu mateka y'isi", ku ya 23 Mutarama hatangajwe gahunda yo guhagarika ingendo zijya no ziva mu mujyi wa Wuhan, nyuma y'aho yongeraho izindi 15 mu ntara ya Hubei, bigira ingaruka ku bantu bagera kuri miliyoni 57.
Imodoka z'abantu ku giti cyabo zarabuzanyijwe mu mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (itariki ya 25 Mutarama) byahagaritswe mu duce twinshi.
Abategetsi kandi batangaje ko hari kubakwa ibitaro by'agateganyo, ibitaro bya Huoshenshan, byuzuye mu minsi 10.
