Ingamba zo gukora ingendo ku munsi umwe zarakorowe muri Hubei, usibye Wuhan, nyuma y'amezi abiri ibihe bidasanzwe byatangiye. Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira binyuze muri visa cyangwa abafite ibyangombwa by'abatuye bizahagarikwa guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, nta makuru yihariye y'igihe iyi politiki izavaho.
Abashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba visa muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsula y'Ubushinwa.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yashishikarije ubucuruzi n'inganda gufungura ku ya 30 Werurwe, kandi itanga inguzanyo ku bigo by'ubucuruzi. Inama y'Igihugu yatangaje umunsi wo kwibuka utangira n'iminota itatu y'agahenge ku isaha ya saa kumi n'ebyiri z'umugoroba ku ya 4 Mata, bihuye n'umunsi mukuru wa Qingming, nubwo leta y'igihugu yasabye imiryango kugaragaza icyubahiro kuri interineti nk'uko bakurikiza ifungwa ry'umubiri mu kwirinda ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyongera.
COVID-19 yemejwe ko yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020 iturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko habayeho kuzamuka gukomeye kw'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare, ahanini biterwa n'amateraniro yabereye i Daegu y'umuteguro mushya w'idini uzwi nka Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Abayoboke ba Shincheonji bari baje i Daegu baturutse i Wuhan bakekwaho kuba ari bo bateje iki cyorezo.
Kugeza ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke 9,336 b'iryo torero, abantu 1,261 cyangwa abagera kuri 13% batangaje ibimenyetso.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abarwayi barenga 2,000 bemejwe baramaze kuvugwa muri Koreya, biyongera ku 3,150 ku ya 29 Gashyantare.
Ibigo byose bya gisirikare bya Koreya y'Epfo byashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu basanze basanzwemo virusi.
Amasaha y'indege na yo yagize ingaruka bityo agenda ahinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda ifatwa nk'iyogeye cyane kandi iteganyijwe cyane ku isi yo gupima abaturage kugira ngo bamenye virusi, no gushyira mu kato abantu bose banduye no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abantu bahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo gupima burimo kwibwirako byanze bikunze ibimenyetso by'abashya bavuye mu bindi bihugu binyuze muri porogaramu igendanwa, gupima virusi ku muyobozi ushize ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima butuma abantu bagera ku 20,000 bapimwa buri munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo ifatwa nk'ifashe neza mu kugenzura icyorezo nubwo itarimo gushyira mu kato umujyi wose.
Abenshi mu baturage ba Koreya bashyize umukono ku nyandiko yo gusaba ko Moon yirukanwa ku byo bavuga ko ari uburyo Leta ikoresha nabi iki cyorezo, cyangwa se bashimira uburyo yabyitwayemo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo ifite umubare muto w'abandura ku munsi mu byumweru bine bishize.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe byatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, abavuye mu mahanga bose bazajya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ibitangazamakuru ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye ibyifuzo by'ubufasha mu gupima virusi biturutse mu bihugu 121 bitandukanye.
Irani yatangaje umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko yanduye SARS-CoV-2 ku ya 19 Gashyantare i Qom, aho Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi bw'Ubuvuzi yavuze ko abantu babiri bapfuye nyuma yaho kuri uwo munsi.
Ingamba z'ibanze leta yatangaje zirimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, siporo, n'amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, no gufunga kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yashyizeho miliyari eshanu z'amadolari y'Amerika yo kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato uturere twatewe n'icyorezo, kandi ko abantu bonyine ari bo bazajya mu kato.
Gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi yatangajwe muri Werurwe, nubwo imodoka nyinshi hagati y'imijyi mbere ya Nowruz y'umwaka mushya wa Peresi zikomeje.
Kurya Shia muri Qom biracyakinguye ku bashyitsi kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020.
Nubwo hari ibivugwa ko iki cyorezo cyateye muri Irani, ibihugu birenga icumi byongeye gukurikirana abanduye muri Irani ku ya 28 Gashyantare, byerekana ko icyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha abanduye 388 leta ya Irani yari imaze gutangaza kugeza icyo gihe.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yari ifunze, aho 23 mu bayigize 290 bari bavuyeyo bagaragaweho virusi ku ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye inzego z'ubugenzacyaha za Irani kurekura nta mananiza abarwanashyaka baharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe bazira imyigaragambyo y'amahoro, no kurekura imfungwa zose zikwiriye mu gihe gito.
Yavuze ko hari ibyago byinshi byo kwandura virusi mu bigo bifunze nk'ibigo by'ifungwa, aho usanga nta buvuzi buhagije.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko hapfuye abantu 100 ku munsi, umubare munini w'abantu bavuzwe muri icyo gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Nibura abanyapolitiki 12 n'abakozi ba leta cyangwa abahozeho barapfuye bazize iki cyorezo kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari ifite abarwayi bashya 50 buri saha n'urupfu rushya buri minota icumi bitewe na coronavirus.
Nk'uko bivugwa n'abayobozi ba OMS, bishoboka ko hari abantu bakubye incuro eshanu abo muri Irani.
Byongeye kandi, byatangaje ko ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'icyo gihugu bwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya virusi.
Komisiyo nkuru y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ishinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu, yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu bigabanywa ku bihugu byazahajwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Icyorezo cyemejwe ko cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubwo abakerarugendo babiri b'Abashinwa bageragezwaga bagasanga baranduye SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Abarwayi batangiye kwiyongera cyane, bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose zijya n'iziva mu Bushinwa kandi igatangaza ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe.
Nyuma yaho, havumbuwe amatsinda y'abantu batandukanye banduye COVID-19, hatangira ku bantu 16 bemejwe ko banduye muri Lombardy ku ya 21 Gashyantare. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya ry'itegeko ryo gukumira icyorezo, harimo no gushyira mu kato abantu barenga 50,000 baturutse mu turere 11 dutandukanye two mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yagize ati "Mu karere k'icyorezo, kwinjira no gusohoka ntibizemewe.
Gufunga ibikorwa by'akazi n'imyidagaduro byatangijwe muri ako gace".Ku ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza zose zifunga burundu mu gihugu cyose ubwo u Butaliyani bwageraga ku bantu 100 bapfuye.
Imikino yose ikomeye, harimo n'imikino ya Serie A, yagombaga kubera mu nzu kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yahagaritswe burundu mu gihe cy'ukwezi.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse guhagarika ibikorwa hafi ya byose by'ubucuruzi uretse amasoko manini n'amavuriro. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani cy'Abanazeziya, Analgesia, Resuscitation na Remedies (SIAARTI) cyasohoye inama y'imyifatire y'ubuvuzi ku bijyanye n'amabwiriza y'isuku ashobora gukoreshwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, u Butaliyani bwaje kurenga u Bushinwa bufite umubare munini w'abantu bapfa bazize coronavirus ku isi nyuma yo gutangaza ko abantu 3,405 bapfuye bazize iki cyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Uburusiya bwohereje indege icyenda za gisirikare zifite ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
