Twahawe amabwiriza yo kugerageza no gutuma ubwo butumwa buvugwa mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo inama n'ibiganiro by'abanyamakuru no kugaragara kuri televiziyo. "Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byatangaje ko ibikorwa by'Ubushinwa byo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byugarijwe na virusi ari bimwe mu bikorwa by'ipfobya byo kwigarurira isi.
