Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko yatoye uburyo bwo kwemerera minisitiri w'intebe, Viktor Orbán, gutegeka ku mugaragaro, guhagarika inteko ishinga amategeko n'amatora no guhana abafatwaho gukwirakwiza amakuru atari yo kuri virusi no ku buryo leta yakemuye iki kibazo.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus cyabayeho kubera ibibazo by'ibura ry'ibicuruzwa, biterwa no gukoresha ibikoresho byo kurwanya icyorezo ku isi hose, kugura ibintu mu buryo bwo guhangayika, no guhungabanya ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikoresho.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze umuburo ku bijyanye n'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitewe n'ubwiyongere bw'abakoresha n'ibiza by'abaguzi.
Mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'igihugu, hari n'aho abantu bagurishije ibintu byinshi cyane, bituma ibigega by'ibikoresho by'ibanze birushaho gusakara, urugero nk'ibiribwa, ibikoresho byo mu bwiherero n'amazi yo mu macupa, bituma habaho ubukene.
