Nubwo umubare munini w'abanduye COVID-19 mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu ntara ya Wuhan, ndetse n'ibyifuzo bikomeye by'ibiribwa, utwo turere twombi twaravuye mu bukene bukabije bw'ibiribwa.
Ingamba zafashwe n'Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya ubucuruzi butemewe n'amategeko bw'ibintu by'ingenzi zagize icyo zigeraho, zivanaho ibura ry'ibiribwa bikomeye byari byitezwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Ubutaliyani bw'amajyaruguru bufite umusaruro ukomeye w'ubuhinzi ntibubonye igabanuka rikomeye, ariko ibiciro bishobora kwiyongera nk'uko byemezwa n'abahagarariye inganda.
