Mu gusubiza, habayeho ingamba zikomeye zo gutanga serivisi zindi binyuze mu buryo bwa digitale. Ikindi cyago giherutse kandi kigenda kirushaho kwiyongera kubera icyorezo ni ukuhagarika serivisi z'idini, ibirori bikomeye mu mikino, n'ibindi bikorwa by'imibanire, nk'ibirori by'umuziki n'ibitaramo, amaseminari y'ikoranabuhanga, n'ibitaramo by'imideri.
Ikigo cya Vatican cyatangaje ko ibirori byo kwizihiza Icyumweru gitagatifu i Roma, byabaga mu cyumweru cya nyuma cya Lenti cy'igihe cy'ububabare bwa gikristo, byahagaritswe.
Abasenyeri benshi basabye abakristo bakuze kuguma mu rugo aho kujya mu Misa ku Cyumweru; amadini amwe na amwe yateguye amasengesho y'itorero ku maradiyo, kuri interineti cyangwa kuri televiziyo mu gihe andi atanga amasengesho yo gusengera mu nzira.
Kubera ko Musenyeri wa Kiliziya Gatolika y'i Roma yafunze insengero n'amatorero mato ndetse n'ahantu hazwi nka St. Peter's Square hakurwaho abayoboke b'abakristo, izindi nzego z'amadini na zo zahagaritse imirimo kandi zigabanya amateraniro rusange mu nsengero, mu nsengero, mu masinagogi, mu nsengero no mu bubiko.
Minisitiri w'Ubuzima wa Irani yatangaje ko amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu yahagaritswe mu duce twatewe n'icyorezo maze imva ziza gufungwa, mu gihe Arabiya Sawudite yabujije abanyamahanga n'abaturage bayo kwinjira mu nsengero za Mecca na Medina.
Iki cyorezo cyateje ihungabana rikomeye cyane ku ngengabihe y'imikino ku isi kuva mu ntambara ya kabiri y'isi.
Imikino myinshi ikomeye y'imikino yahagaritswe cyangwa ihagarikwa, harimo UEFA Champions League 201920, Premier League 201920, UEFA Euro 2020, shampiyona ya NBA 201920 n'umwaka wa NHL 201920.
Icyorezo cyateje ibibazo gahunda y'imikino ya Olympic y'umwaka wa 2020, yari iteganyijwe gutangira mu mpera za Nyakanga; Komite Mpuzamahanga ya Olimpiki yatangaje ku ya 24 Werurwe ko iri rushanwa "rizasubikwa ku itariki nyuma ya 2020 ariko bitarenze impeshyi ya 2021".
Ibi byatumye abenshi mu bakinnyi b'amahirwe bahindukirira imbuga za interineti, aho imbuga nyinshi z'imikino yo kuri interineti zanditse ko habayeho kuzamuka kw'ibiciro by'abashaka kwiyandikisha.
Amakinamico menshi akomeye nka Broadway nayo yahagaritse ibitaramo byose.
Bamwe mu bahanzi barimo gushaka uburyo bwo gukomeza gukora no gusangira ibihangano byabo kuri interineti nk'uburyo bwo guhitamo ibikorwa bisanzwe byo guhererekanya imbonankubone, nko gukora ibitaramo byo guhererekanya imbonankubone cyangwa gukora "ibirori" bishingiye kuri interineti ku bahanzi kugirango batange, bakwirakwize kandi bamenyekanishe ibihangano byabo.
Kuri interineti, ibintu byinshi byo kuri interineti byiganjemo coronavirus byatangiye gukwirakwira ubwo abantu benshi bahindukiraga bakigira ibisanzwe kandi bishimishije mu gihe hari ibibazo.
Kuva COVID-19 yatangira, ivangura, ivangura ry'abanyamahanga n'ivangura byarazamutse ku bantu bakomoka mu Bushinwa no muri Aziya y'Iburasirazuba, no ku bantu bakomoka mu duce dukonje cyane two mu Burayi, Amerika n'ahandi.
Ibihe by'ubwoba, gushidikanya no gukabya byaravuzwe mu bihugu byinshi, cyane cyane mu Burayi, Aziya y'iburasirazuba, Amerika ya Ruguru no mu karere ka Aziya na Pasifika.
Raporo yo mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare (igihe abenshi mu barwayi bari bakiri mu Bushinwa) yagaragaje umwuka w'ivangura wagaragajwe mu matsinda atandukanye ku isi avuga ko Abashinwa bakwiriye kwandura virusi cyangwa bakemera ibyo bavuga ko ari uguhorwa mu buryo bukwiriye.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byo muri Afurika na byo byarabonye ukwiyongera kw'imyitwarire yo kwamagana Ubushinwa.
