Ibizamini bya laboratwari by'indwara y'ubuhumekero ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi itera SARS-CoV-2 birimo uburyo bwo gutahura ko virusi ihari ndetse n'uburyo bwo gutahura abasirikare barwanya umubiri bagaragara mu guhangana n'ubwandu.
Kuba virusi yari mu cyitegererezo byemejwe na RT-PCR, igaragaza RNA ya coronavirus.
Ibizamini ni umwihariko kandi byakozwe gusa mu gushaka RNA ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2.
Ikoreshwa mu kwemeza ubwandu bushya cyangwa bukomeje.
Kumenya antibody (serology) birashobora gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini by'abasirikare b'umubiri bigaragaza umubare w'abarwayi bamaze kwandura, harimo n'abafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyane ku buryo batabivuga cyangwa abafite ibimenyetso.
Ibipimo by'urupfu kubera indwara nyayo n'urwego rw'ubushobozi bw'ingingo mu baturage bishobora kumenyekana biturutse ku bisubizo by'ibi bizamini.
Kubera ibipimo bike, kugeza muri Werurwe 2020 nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yiringirwa ku bijyanye n'ubwandu bwa virusi mu baturage bacyo.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyigeze kigerageza abantu barenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini mu mibare y'ibipimo byakozwe mu bihugu bitandukanye.
Ubu bushobozi kandi bushobora kugira ingaruka ku mibare y'urupfu rw'abanduye, ishobora kuba yararenze urugero mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Gukoresha uburyo bwo gusubiza mu buryo bwa polymerase chain reaction reverse transcription (rRT-PCR) mu gihe nyacyo, ibizamini bishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero byafashwe hakoreshejwe uburyo butandukanye, harimo ibipimo bya nasopharyngeal na ibipimo by'amahembe.
Umwanzuro ubusanzwe uba uriho mu masaha make cyangwa iminsi ibiri.
Ibizamini bya RT-PCR bikorwa hakoreshejwe ibipimo by'umwenge w'umwenge byemezwa gusa mu byumweru bya mbere by'indwara.
Nyuma virusi ishobora kugenda mu muhogo ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ku bantu banduye bapimwe mu gice cya kabiri, ikindi ni uko ibipimo bishobora gukurwa mu nzira y'umwuka hakoreshejwe catheter yo guhumeka cyangwa se hakoreshejwe ibipimo by'ibipimo by'ibipimo by'ibipimo by'ibipimo.
Imwe mu ngero za mbere za PCR yakozwe muri Charité i Berlin muri Mutarama 2020 ikoresheje uburyo bwo gusubiza inyuma inyandiko y'igisubizo cya polyemerase (rRT-PCR) mu gihe nyacyo, kandi yabaye ishingiro ry'udupaki 250,000 tuzajya dutangwa n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS).
Ubwongereza nabwo bwakoze ikizamini tariki 23 Mutarama 2020. Ikigo cyo muri Koreya y'Epfo cya Kogenebiotech cyakoze icyuma cyo gupima SARS-CoV-2 gishingiye kuri PCR, icyiciro cy'ubuvuzi (PowerChek Coronavirus) ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
Yashakishije ubwoko bwa "E" busangirwa na koronavirusi zose za beta, n'ubwoko bwa RdRp bwihariye SARS-CoV-2. Mu Bushinwa, BGI Group ni imwe mu bigo bya mbere byahawe uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihuse n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu gishinzwe Ibikoresho by'Ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa ku bikoresho byo gupima SARS-CoV-2 bishingiye kuri PCR. Muri Amerika, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyatanze Urupapuro rw'Igenzura rwa RT-PCR rwa Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) mu gihe cy'igihe cya vuba ku bigo by'ubuvuzi rusange binyuze mu ikoranabuhanga rya International Reagent Resource.
Kimwe mu bipimo bitatu bya jenoside mu mpapuro za kera z'ibizamini byateje ingaruka zidahamye kubera ibipimo by'ibipimo byangiritse, n'ibizamini by'imipfunda y'amacupa muri CDC i Atlanta; ibi byatanze ku kigereranyo cy'ibipimo 100 ku munsi byakozwe neza muri Gashyantare 2020;
Ibizamini bikoresha ibice bibiri ntibyashoboraga kwemezwa ko ari ibyo kwizerwa kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, kandi mbere yaho, ibigo by'ubushakashatsi bya leta n'ibyaho ntibyemerewe gutangira ibizamini.
Iki cyiciro cy'igeragezwa cyemejwe n'ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti ku buryo bw'ibanze (FDA) ku buryo cyemewe n'amategeko.
Guhera ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, LabCorp yatangaje ko hari ibipimo bya COVID-19 bishingiye kuri RT-PCR bizatangwa mu gihugu hose.
Quest Diagnostics na yo yashyizeho uburyo bwo gupima COVID-19 mu gihugu hose guhera ku ya 9 Werurwe 2020.
Nta mupaka w'ubwinshi watangajwe; ikorwa ry'ibipimo n'imikorere bigomba gukorwa hakurikijwe ibisabwa na CDC.
Mu Burusiya, ibizamini bya COVID-19 byakozwe kandi bitangwa n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cy'Ubushakashatsi mu by'Ubwandu n'Ikoranabuhanga (VECTOR).
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020 iki kizamini cyanditswe na Serivisi y'Igihugu y'Ubugenzuzi mu Buzima. Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, Mayo Clinic yatangaje ko imaze gukora ikizamini cyo gutahura ubwandu bwa COVID-19. Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, Roche Diagnostics yahawe uruhushya na FDA rwo gukora ikizamini gishobora gukorwa mu masaha 3.5 mu mibare myinshi, bityo ikemerera imashini imwe gukora ibizamini bigera ku 4,128 mu masaha 24.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa (EUA) kuri Abbott Laboratories kugirango ikore ibizamini kuri Abbott m2000 system; FDA yari yaratanze uruhushya rusa n'urwo kuri Hologic, LabCorp, na Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Cepheid yahawe EUA na FDA ku isuzuma ryamaze iminota 45.
FDA yemeje ikizamini gikoresha ikoranabuhanga ryo kwagura isothermal nucleic acid aho gukoresha PCR.
Kubera ko ibi bizamini bidasaba ko habaho ibihe byinshi by'ubushyuhe buhindagurika, ubu buryo bushobora gutanga ibisubizo byiza mu gihe cy'iminota itanu n'ibisubizo bibi mu gihe cy'iminota 13.
Ubu hari ibyuma bigera ku 18,000 muri Amerika, kandi Abbott yiteze kwihutisha umusaruro kugira ngo ishobore gutanga ibizamini 50,000 ku munsi. Ibizamini bikoresha umuti wa monoclonal wifatanya mu buryo bwihariye na proteino nucleocapsid (N protein) ya coronavirus nshya biri gukorwa muri Taiwan, mu byiringiro ko bizatanga ibisubizo mu minota 15 kugeza 20 nk'ibizamini bya mbere bya grippe.
Muri Werurwe 2020 isuzuma ryanditse ryasoje rivuga ko "amashusho y'ibere afite agaciro gake mu gusuzuma mu byiciro bya mbere, mu gihe ibipimo bya CT [computed tomography] bishobora kuba byarabonetse mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira".
Ibimenyetso bya CT birimo kubura kw'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri byinshi by'ibirahuri bibiri hamwe n'ibisate by'ibisazi, bidasa n'ibisate by'ibirahuri.
Kwiganzura kw'udutsi tw'imbere, gufungura no guhuza bigerwaho uko indwara igenda itera imbere.
Ubushakashatsi bwagereranyije PCR na CT i Wuhan mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo cy'ubu bwemeje ko CT irusha cyane kumva PCR, nubwo idasanzwe, kuko ifite ibintu byinshi byerekana ko ikora na pneumonia n'izindi ndwara.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika cy'Ikoranabuhanga mu by'Imyuka cyatangaje ko "CT itagomba gukoreshwa mu gupima cyangwa nk'igerageza rya mbere ryo gupima COVID-19".
Igice cy'igisubizo cy'umubiri ku cyorezo ni ugukora za antibody zirimo IgM na IgG.
Ibi bishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima ubwandu mu bantu batangiye iminsi 7 cyangwa nyuma yo gutangira kugaragaza ibimenyetso, mu kumenya ubudahangarwa, no mu kugenzura abaturage.
Sisitemu zigezweho z'imikorere yo hejuru mu ma laboratwari menshi y'ubuvuzi zizashobora gukora ibi byiciro ariko kuboneka kwazo bizaterwa n'ibipimo by'umusaruro kuri buri sisitemu.
Ku CLT, hakoreshwa ibipimo by'amaraso y'uruhande rumwe, nubwo ibipimo by'uruhererekane bishobora gukoreshwa mu gukurikirana ibisubizo by'ubushobozi bw'umubiri.
Ku baganga bakora ibizamini byo mu rwego rwa PoCT, amaraso y'urugero rumwe aba yafashwe binyuze mu gukubita uruhu.
Bitandukanye n'uburyo bwa PCR, intambwe yo gutoza ntizikenewe mbere yo gusuzuma. Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, FDA yashyizeho ibigo 29 bitanga amakuru ku kigo nk'uko bikenewe bityo ubu bishobora gutanga ibizamini byabo by'abanduye.
Kugeza ku ya 7 Mata 2020, ikigo kimwe gusa nicyo cyijejwe na FDA munsi y'uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa.Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, Euroimmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics na Epitope Diagnostics byahawe uburenganzira bw'Uburayi ku bikoresho byabo by'igerageza, bishobora gutahura antibody za IgG na IgA kuri virusi mu cyitegererezo cy'amaraso.
