Muri ibyo bigo 16, 7 biri muri Aziya, 5 biri mu Burayi, 2 biri muri Afurika, 1 muri Amerika ya Ruguru na 1 muri Australia.
Mu mbonerahamwe ikurikira, inkingi "Positive as % test" igira ingaruka ku ngamba z'igihugu mu gupima.
Ibihugu bikora ibizamini ku bantu bavurwa gusa, bibonamo igipimo cyo hejuru cy'ibipimo birimo ibimenyetso by'ubwandu ugereranyije n'ibihugu bikora ibizamini ku baturage bose, batagaragaza ibimenyetso cyangwa batabigaragaza, ibindi byose ni kimwe.
Gukaraba intoki (cyangwa gukaraba intoki), nanone bizwi nka isuku y'intoki, ni igikorwa cyo gusukura intoki z'umuntu kigamije gukuraho umukungugu, ibinure, mikorobe, cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi n'isabuni mu "bihe bikomeye" by'umunsi birinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'indwara y'ibinyigishi n'imyanda, ikwirakwira mu binyoma.
Umuntu ashobora no kwandura indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero nka grippe cyangwa ibicurane bisanzwe, urugero, iyo adasukuye intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, izuru, cyangwa umunwa (nk'urwungano rw'umuhogo).
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi by'umunsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ngombwa harimo: mbere na nyuma yo gukaraba cyane, nyuma yo gusukura umugongo w'umwana cyangwa guhindura indabo, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya mbere na mbere na nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukorana n'inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Iyo nta mazi n'isabune bihari, gukaraba intoki n'imyotsi ni byiza.
Mbere, mu gihe no nyuma yo gutegura amafunguro.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku barwayi.
Nyuma yo guhindura indabo cyangwa se nyuma yo gusukura umwana wakoresheje ubwiherero.
Nyuma yo guhekenya, gukorora cyangwa gutera akabariro.
Iyo umaze gukora ku matungo, ku byokurya byayo cyangwa ku myanda yayo.
Isuku y'amaboko ya muganga yerekeza ku myitozo y'isuku ijyanye n'imikorere ya muganga.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukoresha imiti cyangwa gufata imiti bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Intego y'ibanze yo gukaraba intoki ni ukuzitandukanya n'indwara (indwara, virusi cyangwa ibindi bikoko bishobora gutera indwara) n'ibinyabutabire bishobora guteza akaga cyangwa indwara.
Ibi ni ingenzi cyane cyane ku bantu bakorera ibiribwa cyangwa bakora mu buvuzi, ariko kandi ni ingenzi ku baturage muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane, koronavirusi n'izindi ndwara zandura; gukumira indwara zandura ziterwa n'iseru; kugabanya ubwandu bw'ubuhumekero;
kandi bikagabanya impfu z'abana bavuka mu ngo.
Ubushakashatsi bwo mu 2013 bwagaragaje ko imikoreshereze myiza yo gukaraba intoki yatuma habaho kuzamuka gato mu mikurire y'abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu.
Mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero n'ibisebe ushobora kugabanuka binyuze mu guhindura imyitwarire, urugero nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Iyo ngamba yoroheje ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa kubera iyo ndwara ugera hafi kuri 50%.
Ibiganiro byo gukaraba intoki bishobora kugabanya ibyago byo kurwara diarrhée ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, kandi ibyo bigereranywa no gutanga amazi meza mu duce dukennye.
48% by'igabanuka ry'ibice by'indwara ya diarrhée bishobora kwitirirwa gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni bwo buryo bwonyine bw'ingirakamaro kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda diarrhée n'indwara z'ubuhumekero (ARI), nk'uko bikorwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage ku isi hose.
Imyotsi, ARI ikomeye, ni yo mpamvu ya mbere ihitana abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, ihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Indwara y'ibisebe n'indwara y'ibihaha byombi bihitana abana bagera hafi kuri miriyoni 3.5 buri mwaka.
UNICEF ivuga ko kwimenyereza gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero bishobora kurokora ubuzima bwinshi kurusha urukingo rumwe cyangwa imiti ikoreshwa mu buryo butandukanye, bikagabanya hafi kimwe cya kabiri cy'abapfa kubera iseru n'icya kane cy'abapfa kubera indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye.
Gukaraba intoki bikunze guhuzwa n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku nk'igice cya gahunda y'amazi, isuku n'isuku (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki nabyo bishobora kurinda impetigo yandura binyuze mu guhura n'umuntu imbonankubone.
Ingaruka mbi ntoya yo gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane ni uko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutuma umubiri uhomba bitewe n'uko umubiri uba ufite igifu.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu gihugu cya Danemark mu 2012 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutera itekamutwe, indwara y'uruhu ifite ibibyimba yitwa eczema y'intoki cyangwa dermatite y'intoki, ikunze kugaragara mu bakora mu by'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane nabyo bifatwa nk'ikimenyetso cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu bikomeye by'umunsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ari ngombwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara y'ubuhumekero mu kanwa: nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero (kwiyuhagira, gusama), nyuma yo gusukura umugongo w'umwana (guhindura indabo), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya no mbere/nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukorana n'inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Indi minsi yo gukaraba intoki neza mu kwirinda kwandura indwara harimo mbere na nyuma yo gukemura igikomere cyangwa igikomere; nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora, cyangwa guhumeka; nyuma yo gukora ku binure by'inyamaswa cyangwa gukorana n'inyamaswa; no nyuma yo gufata imyanda.
Umubare w'abantu bakoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki ni muto mu bihugu byinshi.
Mu mwaka wa 2015, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku gukaraba intoki mu bihugu 54 bwagaragaje ko ku kigereranyo 38.7% by'ingo zifite akamenyero ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Mu mwaka wa 2014, ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko Arabiya Sawudite ifite igipimo cyo hejuru cya 97 ku ijana; Amerika iri hafi hagati na 77 ku ijana; n'Ubushinwa bufite igipimo cyo hasi cya 23 ku ijana.
Porogaramu y'Ubuzima bw'ingenzi ishyirwa mu bikorwa n'Urwego rw'Uburezi muri Filipine ni urugero rw'ibikorwa byinshi byo guharanira ubuzima n'uburezi bw'abana.
Gucukura udusimba kabiri mu mwaka, hamwe no gukaraba intoki buri munsi n'isabuni, no gusukura amenyo buri munsi n'amazi ya Florida, ni byo by'ingenzi muri iyi gahunda y'igihugu.
Byakorewe muri Indoneziya.
Gukuraho mikorobe ku ruhu bishobora kwiyongera ugushyira isabune cyangwa umuti mu mazi.
Igikorwa cy'ibanze cya sabune n'ibikoresho by'isuku ni ugugabanya inzitizi ku muti, no kongera ubunyunyu.
Amazi yonyine si yo yonyine isukura neza uruhu kuko ibinure na poroteyine, ari byo bice by'ubutaka bw'ibinyabuzima, ntibishobora gukama mu mazi.
Ariko kandi, amazi meza atuma habaho isuku.
Kubera imiterere yayo ishobora kongera gukoreshwa, isabune y'ibumba ishobora kubika mikorobe zatoraguwe mu mikoreshereze yabanjirije.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwakozwe ku kwinjiza za bagiteri mu isabune y'ibishyimbo byanduye bwagaragaje ko kwinjiza bidashoboka kuko za bagiteri zivaho iyo zisukuwe n'ifumbire.
Urubuga rwa CDC rukomeza ruvuga ko "isabuni y'amazi itarimo intoki ari nziza".
Amasabune arwanya za mikorobe afite amajwi menshi mu bantu bashyira imbere ubuzima.
Kugeza ubu nta gihamya igaragaza ko gukoresha imiti yica udukoko cyangwa imiti yica udukoko byatuma habaho ibinyabuzima bidashobora kurwanya imiti.
Nyamara, isabune zica zabakiteri zirimo imiti isanzwe yabakiteri nka triclosan, ifite urutonde rwagutse rw'ibinyabuzima bihangana n'ibice by'umubiri.
Bityo, nubwo ubwoko budafite abanduye butoranyijwe n'isabune z'indwara, zishobora kuba zidafite ingaruka nziza nk'uko byatangajwe.
Usibye surfactants na agent z'uruhu zirinda uruhu, iyi formulations igezweho ishobora kuba irimo aside (acetic acid, ascorbic acid, lactic acid) nk'umuyobozi wa pH, acide benzoate ifite ingufu z'ubuvuzi n'ibindi bikoresho byo guhumura uruhu (aloe vera, vitamine, menthol, ibimera).
Amazi ntabwo ashyushye cyane ku buryo yoza intoki, ntabwo ashyushye cyane ku buryo yica mikorobe.
Bacteria zikubita cyane ku bushyuhe bw'umubiri (37°C).
Ariko kandi, amazi ashyushye n'isabune ni meza cyane kurusha amazi akonje n'isabune mu gukuraho amavuta asanzwe arimo ubutaka n'udukoko.
Bitandukanye n'uko abantu benshi babyizera, ubushakashatsi bwa siyansi bugaragaza ko gukoresha amazi ashyushye nta ngaruka bigira ku kugabanya mikorobe ziri ku biganza.
Umwandazi w'amaboko cyangwa umuti wica udukoko ni umuti wo gusukura intoki udashingiye ku mazi.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, kunywa ibiyobyabwenge byo gusukura intoki bitagikoreshwa amazi (bizwi kandi nka alcohol-based rubbing, antiseptic hand rubbing, cyangwa hand sanitizer) byatangiye gukundwa.
Byinshi bishingiye kuri alkol y'isopropylique cyangwa ethanol yashyizwe hamwe na karubone (polymère ya acrylic acid) mu mazi, cyangwa humctane nka glycerine mu mazi, cyangwa inyanya kugirango byorohereze gukoresha no kugabanya ingaruka zo kumesa za alkol.
Iyo wongeyemo hydrogen peroxide yagabanutse bituma habaho ibindi bintu byongera ubushobozi bwo kurwanya mikorobe.
Gucika inzoga bica mikorobe, mikorobe zidakira imiti myinshi (MRSA na VRE), igituntu na virusi zimwe na zimwe (harimo HIV, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, vaccinia, influenza na hepatite) na fungus.
Umwandazi w'inzoga ufite 70% by'inzoga wica 99,97% (igabanuka rya log 3,5 ringana n'igabanuka rya decibel 35) ry'udukoko two ku maboko nyuma y'amasegonda 30 ukoresheje na 99,99% (igabanuka rya log 4 kugeza kuri 5) ry'udukoko two ku maboko nyuma y'umunota umwe ukoresheje.
Amavuta yo gusukura intoki ku nzoga hafi ya yose nta ngaruka agira kuri virusi yo mu bwoko bwa norovirus (cyangwa Norwalk), intandaro y'indwara y'uruhu isanzwe cyane.
Imbere n'inyuma y'ibiganza byombi no hagati y'imitwe y'intoki zose zirahuzwa mu gihe cy'amasegonda agera kuri 30 kugeza amazi, isupu cyangwa gel byumye.
Inkoryo z'intoki na zo zigomba gukaraba neza, ukazikorakora ku ntoki zombi. Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara gitanga inama yo gukaraba intoki kurusha uko wakoresha umuti wica udukoko, cyane cyane iyo intoki zisa n'izanduye.
Ikoreshwa ry'iyi miti riragenda ryiyongera kubera uburyo bworoshye bwo gukoresha no kwica vuba mikorobe.
Gukoresha kenshi imiti yo gusukura intoki ikoreshwa n'inzoga bishobora gutuma uruhu rukonja keretse iyo emollients na/cyangwa umuti wo guhumura uruhu byongerewe ku buryo.
Ingaruka z'inzoga zimena zishobora kugabanuka cyangwa zikarandurwa no kongera glycerine na/cyangwa izindi emollients mu buryo.
Mu igeragezwa ry'ubuvuzi, imiti yo guhanagura intoki ikoreshwa ku nzoga irimo emoliens yatumye uruhu rutagira uburakari n'umwuma ugereranyije n'isabune cyangwa umuti urwanya mikorobe.
Indwara y'uruhu iterwa n'imyanda, indwara y'umwanda w'inkari cyangwa se indwara y'ubuhumyi cyangwa se indwara y'ubuhumyi.
Kugaragaza ko hari uburyo bwo kugabanya cyane indwara y'uruhu rw'uruhu rwihuta cyane (irritative contact dermatitis) birashimishije cyane ugereranyije no gukoresha isabune n'amazi mu gukaraba intoki.
Igikoresho kitari amazi, nubwo gifite akamaro, nticyeza intoki z'ibinyabuzima, ahubwo kirandura udukoko.
Ibi bituma imiti yo guhanagura intoki idakora neza nk'isabune n'amazi mu kwirinda indwara nyinshi kuko indwara zikomeza kuba ku ntoki.
Imikorere y'imiti yo guhanagura intoki idafite alukoro ishingiye cyane ku byubaka n'uburyo ikoreshwamo, kandi kuva kera ntabwo yageze kuri byinshi ugereranyije n'inzoga n'isuku.
Mu minsi yashize, uburyo bukoresha benzalkonium chloride bwagaragaye ko bufite ibikorwa bya antimicrobial bikomeza kandi byiyongera nyuma yo gukoresha, bitandukanye na alukoro yagaragaye ko igabanuka nyuma yo gukoresha inshuro nyinshi, bishoboka ko biterwa n'imiterere mibi y'uruhu igenda igenda.
Abantu benshi bafite amikoro make ntibashobora kubona isabune, ahubwo bakoresha imyanda cyangwa isaka.
Umwotsi cyangwa ubutaka bishobora kugira ingaruka nziza kurusha gukoresha amazi yonyine ariko bishobora kugira ingaruka nkeya kurusha isabune.
Impungenge ni uko ubutaka cyangwa imyanda byanduzwa n'udukoko dushobora gutuma indwara zikwirakwira aho kugabanya ikwirakwira ryayo.
Umwotsi kandi ni umuti wica udukoko nk'isabune kuko utanga umuti wa alkali iyo uhuye n'amazi.
OMS igira inama ko hari imyanda cyangwa umucanga wafasha mu gusimbuza isabune mu gihe isabune itaboneka.
Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara gitanga inama yo gukaraba intoki neza mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara harimo ibi bikurikira:
Amaboko yuzuye amazi ashyushye cyangwa akonje.
Amazi acuncubuka arasabwa kuko ubwiherero bushobora kwandura, mugihe ubushyuhe bwamazi busa n'aho nta ngaruka.
Gukaraba intoki mu gihe ubikoresha isabune nyinshi, harimo inyuma y'intoki, hagati y'intoki, no munsi y'amano.
Amasabune yirukana mikorobe ku ruhu, kandi ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko abantu bakunda gukaraba intoki neza iyo bakoresheje isabune kurusha uko bakoresha amazi yonyine.
Mujye mufata nibura amasegonda 20.
Gutereka bituma habaho guhinduranya, bifasha gukura mikorobe ku ruhu, kandi guteranya igihe kirekire cyane bituma habaho gutsemba mikorobe nyinshi.
Jya uyuhanagura neza mu mazi arimo amazi.
Gukaraba mu kabati bishobora kongera kwanduza intoki.
Zishyireho umutsima cyangwa uzihe umwuka.
Ibiganza byumye kandi byumye biroroshye kongera kwanduza. Inzoka nini, intoki, hagati y'intoki no munsi y'inkokora ni ibice by'umubiri byama byirengagizwa.
Zishobora kuba zibitse mu minwa y'impimbano n'amabara y'inkokora.
Losiyo yo kwisiga iraterwa inkunga yo kwirinda ko intoki zisaka; uruhu rwumye rushobora kwangiza uruhu rushobora kongera ibyago byo kwanduza.
Hari uburyo bwinshi buhendutse bwo koroshya gukaraba intoki niba nta mazi yo mu musarani na/cyangwa isabune bihari, urugero nko kohereza amazi mu bibindi by'amazi cyangwa inkono zifite imyobo ikwiriye no/cyangwa gukoresha imyanda niba ari ngombwa mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere. Iyo amazi ari make (nk'amashuri cyangwa uduce two mu cyaro mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere), hari ibisubizo bikingira amazi nka "impyiko z'impu" n'ubundi buryo buhendutse.
Imashini y'umuvure ni ikoranabuhanga ryoroshye rikoresha imigozi ifunze n'umugozi, n'inkokora zikoreshwa n'amaguru kugira ngo basuke amazi make ku ntoki n'isabune.
Igice cyingenzi cyo gusukura intoki ni ugusukura intoki neza, ariko hari impaka ku buryo bwiza bwo guteka mu bwiherero rusange.
Ubushakashatsi bugenda bwiyongera bugaragaza ko utwenda two gusukura dukoreshejwe impapuro twera cyane kurusha utwuma two koza intoki dukoreshwa n'amashanyarazi tuboneka mu byumba byinshi byo kwiyuhagiriramo.
Mu mwaka wa 2008, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Westminster, i Londres, bwatewe inkunga n'uruganda rw'impuzamirimo y'impapuro, European Tissue Symposium, bugereranya isuku y'impuzamirimo ikoresha impapuro z'impuzamirimo, ibyuma bishyushya intoki n'ibyuma bishyushya intoki.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumesa intoki n'igikoresho gikonjesha, umubare wa bagiteri mu ntoki z'intoki z'imbere wiyongereyeho 194% na 254% mu biganza.
Kumesa n'imashini zimesa umwuka byazamuye umubare wa bagiteri ku ntoki zo hasi ku kigereranyo cya 42% no ku ntoki ku kigereranyo cya 15%.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumesa intoki ukoresheje umwenda w'impapuro, umubare wa bagiteri ku ruhande rw'iburyo ku gipimo cyagabanutseho 76% na 77% ku rutoki.
Umwuka w'umwuka wa jet, uhumeka umwuka uva mu cyumba ku muvuduko wa 180 m/s (650 km/h; 400 bsj), ushobora guhumeka mikorobe mu ntoki no mu cyumba kandi bishobora kwangiza abandi bakoresha ubwiherero n'aho ubwiherero buri metero 2.
Gukoresha umwumazi w'amaboko ushyushye w'umwuka utuma mikorobe zikwirakwira kugera kuri metero 0.25 z'umwumazi.
Mu mwaka wa 2005, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na TÜV Produkt und Umwelt bwakoze ku buryo butandukanye bwo kumesa intoki.
Impinduka zikurikira zagaragaye mu mubare wa bagiteri nyuma yo kumesa intoki:
Hariho ababikora batandukanye, kandi ibyo bikoresho bigereranywa n'impapuro z'ibyatsi.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje agatambaro ko kwiyuhagira bigira ingaruka nziza mu gihe uri mu rugendo igihe nta isabune n'amazi bihari.
Umwandazi w'intoki ufite inzoga ugomba kuba ufite nibura 60% bya alukoro.
Gukaraba intoki mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi byari byarabaye itegeko igihe umuganga w'Umunyahungariya witwa Ignaz Semmelweis yabonaga ko ari ingirakamaro (mu 1846) mu kwirinda indwara mu bitaro.
Hari ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki biburira abakozi b'ibitaro ko bagomba gukaraba intoki iyo bibagiwe.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko kuyinywa byagabanya ubwandu.
Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi byibuze amasegonda 15, ukoresheje isabune n'amazi menshi cyangwa gel yo gukaraba no gusokoza buri gice cy'ukuboko.
Ukuboko kugomba gusukwa hamwe n'intoki z'umuntu winjiye nabi.
Niba hari umwanda munsi y'inkokora, buroshi y'ubwoya ishobora gukoreshwa mu kuwukuraho.
Kubera ko mikorobe zishobora kuguma mu mazi ku ntoki, tugomba kubanza kuzisukura neza no kuzisahura kugeza zumye n'utwuma duto.
Nyuma yo kumesa intoki, umwenda w'impapuro ugomba gukoreshwa mu gufunga amazi (kandi ukingura usohoke niba ari ngombwa).
Ibi bituma intoki zidakomeza kwanduza iyo zikoze ku kintu.
Gukaraba intoki mu buzima bw'abantu bigamije gukuraho mikorobe ziterwa n'indwara ("currents") no kwirinda ko zikwirakwira.
Ikinyamakuru New England Journal of Medicine cyatangaje ko gukaraba intoki bidakomeje ari ibintu bitemewe mu nzego nyinshi z'ubuvuzi, aho abaganga benshi n'abaforomo bibagirwa gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku barwayi, bityo bakwirakwiza mikorobe.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki neza n'indi mirimo yoroshye bishobora kugabanya umubare w'indwara z'amaraso zifitanye isano n'imashini z'umuyoboro wa za kateri ku kigero cya 66%. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryasohoye inyandiko igaragaza amahame agenga gukaraba intoki no kuzisiga mu nzego z'ubuzima.
Amategeko agenga isuku y'amaboko y'iri shyirahamwe kandi araboneka ku rubuga rwayo kugira ngo abantu bayagezeho.
Ubushakashatsi bukenewe bwakozwe na Whitby et al.
Ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi bishobora gupima no kwemeza isuku y'amaboko, niba hagikenewe kwerekana ko amategeko yubahirijwe.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima rifite "Ibihe bitanu" byo gukaraba intoki:
nyuma yo guhura n'amaraso/amazi yo mu mubiri
mbere yo gukora isuku, kandi
Nyuma yo kuvura umurwayi. Kongeramo imiti yica udukoko mu isabune (isabune "yivura" cyangwa "antimicrobial") bituma imyanda yo mu ntoki ihita ipfa.
Kugira ngo 'mwoze' intoki z'umuntu mu gihe cyo kubagwa, hakenewe imashini ishobora gufunguka no gufunga nta gukorakora intoki, hari amazi yo gusukura arimo chlorhexidine cyangwa iodine, utwuma two gukaraba twanduye two kumesa intoki nyuma yo gukaraba, n'udupira twanduye two gusukura no gusukura n'ibindi bikoresho byanduye byo gusukura munsi y'amanota.
Ibintu byose by'agaciro bigomba gukurwaho.
Ubu buryo bukenera gukaraba intoki no ku maboko kugeza ku nkokora, ubusanzwe mu minota 2-6
Igihe kirekire cyo gusukura (iminota 10) ntikikenewe.
Mu gihe cyo gukaraba, amazi yo mu ntoki hasi agomba guhagarikwa kugira ngo adasubira mu ntoki.
Iyo bamaze gukaraba intoki, bazisahura n'umwenda w'isuku kandi bambare imyenda y'ubuvuzi.
Kugira ngo utagenda wiruka, ni byiza gukaraba intoki cyangwa gukoresha imiti yica udukoko mbere na nyuma yo kuvura umuntu urwaye.
Mu kugenzura indwara z'ibicurane mu bitaro, byagaragaye ko inyungu zikomeye zo gukaraba intoki zituruka ku masaha 20%, kandi ko hari inyungu nke cyane z'inyongera ziboneka iyo umubare w'abantu bakaraba intoki wiyongereyeho 35%.
Gukaraba intoki n'isabune isanzwe bitera indwara zandura zandura mu biryo inshuro zirenga eshatu ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki n'isabune ya antibacteria. Kugereranya gukaraba intoki n'umuti w'inzoga no gukaraba intoki n'isabune ya antibacteria mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30, buri kimwe cyerekana ko gukaraba intoki n'inzoga bigabanya ubwandu bwa bagiteri ku kigero cya 26% kurusha isabune ya antibacteria.
Ariko isabune n'amazi bifite ingaruka nziza kurusha gusukura intoki ku nzoga mu kugabanya virusi ya influenza A H1N1 na Klostridium difficile ku ntoki. Iterabwoba ryo kongera isuku mu buzima busanzwe bushobora kuba rikubiyemo kwigisha abakozi gusukura intoki, kongera iboneka ry'isuku y'intoki ku nzoga, no kuburira abakozi mu nyandiko no mu magambo.
Hakenewe ubushakashatsi bwinshi ku buryo bw'ingamba z'ubuvuzi z'uburyo butandukanye zishobora kugira icyo zigeraho.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki n'isabuni biremerwa nk'uburyo bw'ingirakamaro kandi buhendutse bwo kugera ku buzima bwiza, ndetse no kurya neza.
Icyakora, kutagira amazi meza, isabune cyangwa uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki mu ngo, ku ishuri no mu kazi, bituma kugera ku myitwarire yo gukaraba intoki ku isi hose bigorana.
Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'icyaro muri Afurika, imiyoboro yo gukaraba intoki hafi y'ubwiherero bwa buri wese bwa bwite n'ubwa rubanda ni imbonekarimwe, nubwo hari uburyo buhendutse bwo kubaka aho gukaraba intoki.
Ariko kandi, umubare muto w'abantu bakaraba intoki ushobora guterwa n'akamenyero ko kudashyira amasabune cyangwa amazi mu ntoki.
Guteza imbere no kuburanira gukaraba intoki n'isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku byemezo bya politiki, byongera ubumenyi ku nyungu zo gukaraba intoki kandi bigatuma habamo impinduka mu myitwarire y'abaturage mu gihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo ibi bikore neza, hakenewe kugenzura no gusuzuma.
Isesengura ryagutse ry'ubushakashatsi 70 ryagaragaje ko uburyo bushingiye ku muryango ari bwo bw'ingenzi mu kongera gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikennye, mu gihe ubukangurambaga bwo kwamamaza ku mbuga nkoranyambaga butari bufite akamaro. Urugero rumwe rwo guteza imbere gukaraba intoki mu mashuri ni "Inzira y'inyenyeri eshatu" na UNICEP itera amashuri inkunga yo gufata ingamba zoroshye kandi z'ingengo y'imari kugira ngo abanyeshuri bakarabe intoki n'isabuni, mu bindi bintu by'isuku.
