Guteza imbere aho gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa byo guteza imbere gukaraba intoki bigamije kugabanya indwara n'urupfu mu bana.
Umunsi mpuzamahanga wo gukaraba intoki ni urundi rugero rw'ubukangurambaga bwo gukangurira abantu guhindura imyitwarire. Kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-20, UNICEF yashishikarije abantu gukoresha emoji zo gukaraba intoki.
