Ariko ubushakashatsi bwerekanye ko guteza imbere gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari byo bigabanya amafaranga cyane kurusha ibindi bikorwa byo kuvura amazi n'isuku.
Akamaro ko gukaraba intoki ku buzima bwa muntu  cyane cyane ku bantu bari mu mimerere ishobora guteza ibibazo nk'ababyeyi baherutse kubyara cyangwa abasirikare bakomerekeye mu bitaro  byamenyekanye bwa mbere mu kinyejana cya 19 rwagati n'abapayiniya babiri b'isuku y'intoki: umuganga wo muri Hongiriya Ignaz Semmelweis wakoreraga i Vienne, Austria na Forence Nightingale, "washyizeho ubuvuzi bugezweho" bw'Ubwongereza.
