Gutegeka akaga ko mu kazi ka COVID-19
Gucunga akaga ko mu kazi ka COVID-19 ni uburyo bwo gukoresha ubuvuzi n'umutekano mu kazi mu gucunga akaga ko mu kwirinda icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Gucunga neza akaga ku kazi biterwa n'aho umuntu akorera n'akazi akora, hashingiwe ku gusuzuma ibyago by'isoko y'ubwandu, ubukana bw'indwara mu baturage, n'ibyago by'umukozi ku giti cye ashobora kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo cy'ubwiteganyirize n'ubuzima muri Amerika (OSHA), akazi gashobora guteza ibyago byinshi gafite aho gaherereye ku kazi gafite aho gaherereye mu kazi gaherereye mu baturage n'abandi bakozi, aho ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu zirimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo iyo barwaye, kwitwara neza mu guhumeka, no kugira isuku ya buri gihe no kwanduza udukoko mu kazi.
Akazi gashobora guteza ibyago byo kwandura mu buryo bworoshye gakubiyemo akazi gashobora kuba gasaba guhura kenshi cyangwa kwegera abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kugira COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura bitewe n'ubwandu buriho mu baturage cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Ibyo birimo abakozi bagirana imishyikirano n'abaturage nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorera abaturage benshi, ndetse n'ahantu henshi hacuruzwa ibicuruzwa byinshi.
Gutegeka akaga kuri iri tsinda, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu harimo guhumeka ukoresheje imashini z'umwuka zifite ubushobozi bwo guhanagura umwuka, abashinzwe gukinga gusinzira, no kugira ibikoresho byo kwirinda mu gihe uhuye n'umuntu wanduye COVID-19.
OSHA ifata abakozi bo mu bigo by'ubuvuzi n'iby'amarembo bahura n'abantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 nk'abafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, bikazamuka bikajya ku kigero cyo kurwara cyane iyo abakozi bakoze uburyo bwo gukora aerosol kuri, cyangwa gukusanya cyangwa gukorana ibipimo by'abantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19.
Gutegeka akaga gakwiriye aba bakozi birimo kugenzura ingufu z'ubwubatsi nk'icyumba cy'umwuka gifite umuvuduko utabereye n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bikwiye akazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi mu kazi.
Umukozi ashobora kutaza ku kazi kubera uburwayi, kwita ku bandi cyangwa gutinya ko ashobora guhura n'ibibazo.
Imikorere y'ubucuruzi irashobora guhinduka, haba mu bijyanye n'ibicuruzwa bisabwe, n'uburyo bwo kubona ibicuruzwa (nk'ibicuruzwa byo hanze y'amasaha y'ikirenga cyangwa binyuze mu serivisi yo kohereza cyangwa gutwara).
Amaherezo, kohereza ibicuruzwa mu turere tuzwiho kuba twugarijwe na COVID-19 bishobora guhungabana. Imyiteguro n'igikorwa cyo guhangana n'indwara zandura bishobora gukoreshwa nk'ubuyobozi bw'ingamba zo kwirinda.
Gahunda ikora ku rwego rw'ibyago bijyanye n'ahantu henshi hakorerwa imirimo n'imirimo y'akazi harimo isoko y'ibyago, ibyago bituruka mu rugo no mu baturage, n'ibyago by'umukozi ku giti cye nk'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Nanone kandi, igaragaza ingamba zikenewe kugira ngo icyo cyorezo kiveho, n'ingamba zo guhangana n'ibiza.
Gahunda yo kwitegura no guhangana n'indwara zandura ishobora kuba igengwa n'ibyifuzo by'ingamba z'igihugu cyangwa z'ibihugu.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo harimo kugabanya ubwandu mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zikomeye, gukomeza imikorere y'ubucuruzi, no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bindi bigo byo mu muyoboro wabo w'itangwa ry'ibiribwa.
Ubwiyongere bw'indwara mu baturage aho ubucuruzi buri bugira ingaruka ku bisubizo byafashwe.
Urwego rwo kugenzura impanuka ni urwego rukoreshwa cyane mu buvuzi n'umutekano mu kazi mu gushyira hamwe kugenzura impanuka hakurikijwe ingaruka zabyo.
Iyo hatari ya COVID-19 idashobora gukurwaho, uburyo bwiza bwo kugenzura ni ubuhanga, bukurikirwa n'ubuyobozi, hanyuma hakagira ibikoresho byo kwirinda.
Kugenzura ubwubatsi bikubiyemo gutandukanya abakozi n'ibiza bijyanye n'akazi bidashingiye ku myitwarire y'abakozi, kandi bishobora kuba umuti mwiza cyane wo gushyira mu bikorwa.
Gucunga ubuyobozi ni ihinduka mu buryo bw'imikorere cyangwa mu buryo bw'imikorere bukenera igikorwa cy'umukozi cyangwa umukoresha.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi (PPE) bifatwa nk'ibidakora neza cyane ugereranyije n'ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi n'ibikoresho by'ubuyobozi ariko bishobora gufasha mu kwirinda bimwe mu bintu bishobora gutuma umuntu ahura n'ibiza.
Ubwoko bwose bwa PPE bugomba gutoranywa hashingiwe ku kaga ku mukozi, gushyirwaho neza hakurikijwe uko bikwiye (cth respirator), kwambara neza ku buryo buhoraho, kugenzura buri gihe, kubungabunga no gusimbuza, niba ari ngombwa, no gukuraho neza, gusukura no kubika cyangwa kujugunya kugira ngo wirinde kwanduza.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi ku buzima n'umutekano (OSHA), akazi gashobora guteza ibyago byinshi ni ugukorana n'abantu benshi ndetse n'abandi bakozi.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu zisabwa ahantu hose hakorerwa imirimo zirimo gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi neza, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, amahame agenga imyitwarire y'ubuhumekero arimo kwambara igihe bakoroye no gutitira, gutegura utwenda n'ibikoresho byo guhana imyanda, kwitegura gukora kuri terefone cyangwa mu masaha y'akazi mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, kudashishikariza abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho cyangwa ibikoresho by'abandi, no gukomeza gahunda yo gusukura no kwanduza indwara mu kazi.
Kumenya no gushyira mu kato abantu bashobora kwandura vuba ni intambwe ikomeye mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi mu kazi.
Ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) kirasaba ko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bukomeye baguma mu rugo kugeza igihe badafite umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso by'imibare 24 y'amasaha badafite imiti igabanya umuriro cyangwa imiti itera izindi ndwara, kandi bagakoresha politiki yoroheje yo kuruhuka indwara, yemerera abakozi kuguma mu rugo kwita ku bagize umuryango barwaye, kandi abakozi bamenye aya mabwiriza.
Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, akazi gashobora guteza ibyago byo guhura n'ubwandu buciriritse gakubiyemo akazi gashobora gusaba guhura kenshi cyangwa kwegera cyane abantu bari muri metero esheshatu (1.8 m) z'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kurwara COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2 bitewe n'ubwandu bukomeje kuba mu baturage bari hafi y'aho ibikorwa bikorerwa, cyangwa kubera ko uwo muntu aherutse gukora ingendo mpuzamahanga mu duce dufite ubwandu bwa COVID-19.
Ibi birimo abakozi bahuye n'abaturage nk'abanyeshuri, ahantu hakorerwamo abantu benshi hamwe n'ahantu henshi hacuruzwa ibicuruzwa byinshi. Gutegeka kwa injeniyeri kuri iri tsinda hamwe n'itsinda ry'abari mu kaga gakomeye birimo gushyiraho filtrateur y'umwuka ikora neza, kongera umuvuduko w'umwuka, gushyiraho inzitizi z'umubiri nka za plastiki zirinda guswera no gushyiraho amadirishya y'abashoferi ku bakiriya. Gutegeka kwa guverinoma kuri iri tsinda hamwe n'itsinda ry'abari mu kaga gakomeye birimo gushishikariza itsinda ry'abakozi barwaye kuguma mu rugo, gusimbuza imibonano mpuzabitsina ihuza amaso n'amaso itumanaho, gushyiraho guhuzagurika, guhagarika ingendo zidakenewe mu bihe by'ingenzi hamwe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje, gukora gahunda y'itumanaho ryihutirwa harimo abakozi b'umushyikirano bitabiriye ibibazo, guha abakozi uburere bugezweho n'imyitozo ku mpamvu z'ibyago bya COVID-19 no kwitwara neza, gutoza abakoresha imyenda n'imyambaro ikingira ku buryo bwo kwambara, no guharanira kwirinda aho bakorera, kandi bagatanga amabwiriza yo kwirinda aho bakorera, wenda bagakoresha udupfukamunwa cyangwa ibindi bikoresho by'akazi, bakoresheje ibiganza, ibikoresho byo guhana n'amaso, ibikoresho byo guhana n'amaso hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho bikenewe mu kazi, hamwe n'ibikorwa by'abantu benshi.
Abakozi bari muri iri tsinda ry'abashobora guhura n'ibibazo by'uburwayi ntibakunze gukenera gukoresha ibyuma byo guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, ingamba nziza zo kurinda abakozi n'abandi bagenzi zirimo gutandukanya uwo muntu urwaye n'abandi bantu mu ntera ya metero 6, guha abakozi bo mu ndege inshingano zo kumwitaho, no guha umurwayi agapfukamunwa cyangwa kumusaba ko apfuka umunwa n'izuru n'utubari mu gihe akoroye cyangwa atetse.
Abakozi ba kabin bagombye kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'imiti tw'imishwaro igihe bavura umushoferi urwaye cyangwa bakora ku mazi yo mu mubiri cyangwa ku bintu bishobora kwandura, kandi wenda n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi by'inyongera mu gihe umushoferi urwaye afite umuriro, ikorora rikomeje cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Inkweto n'ibindi bintu bikoreshwa rimwe bigomba kujugunywa mu mufuka w'ibinyabuzima, kandi imyanya yanduye igomba gusukurwa no guhanagurwa nyuma yaho. Ku ngendo z'ubucuruzi zirimo ubwato bw'urugendo n'ubundi bwato bw'abagenzi, kugenzura akaga birimo gusubika urugendo iyo urwaye, kwigunga no kumenyesha ikigo nderabuzima cyo ku bwato ako kanya iyo umuntu afite umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso igihe ari mu bwato.
Ku ishuri n'ibigo byita ku bana, CDC itera inkunga gufunga by'igihe gito kugira ngo hasuzumwe cyangwa hakurweho indwara y'ibicurane niba umuntu wanduye yari mu nyubako y'ishuri hatitawe ku gukwirakwira mu baturage.
Iyo ubwandu mu baturage bufite igipimo cyo hasi kugeza ku gipimo cyo hagati, ingamba zo gutandukanya abantu n'abandi zishobora gushyirwa mu bikorwa nko guhagarika ingendo zo mu murima, guterana hamwe n'andi materaniro manini nka porogaramu z'imyitozo ngororamubiri n'amasomo ya korali cyangwa kurya mu kabari, kongera intera hagati y'ameza, igihe cyo kugera no kuva mu byiciro, kugabanya abashyitsi batari ngombwa, no gukoresha ahantu hatandukanye ho gukorera ibiro by'ubuzima ku bana bafite ibimenyetso nk'ibicurane.
