Ku bantu bakusanya ibipimo by'ubuhumekero, bavura cyangwa batwara abarwayi ba COVID-19 badafite uburyo bwo gukora aerosol, OMS itera inkunga y'uko bakoresha udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi, udukingirizo tw'amaso, cyangwa udukingirizo tw'amaso, imyenda n'amatako.
Niba hakorwa uburyo bwo gukora aerosol, agapfukamunwa ko kubaga gasimbuzwa N95 cyangwa respirateur FFP2.
Kubera ko ku isi hose nta bikoresho bya PPE bihagije biboneka, OMS irasaba kugabanya cyane ibyo bikoresho binyuze mu kwivuza kure, inzitizi z'umubiri nk'amadirishya asobanutse, kwemerera gusa abashinzwe kwita ku barwayi kwinjira mu byumba by'abarwayi ba COVID-19, gukoresha gusa ibikoresho bya PPE bikenewe mu kazi runaka, gukomeza gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubuhumekero bimwe bidasubitswe mu gihe urimo kwita ku barwayi benshi bafite indwara imwe, kugenzura no guhuza uruziga rw'ibikoresho bya PPE, no kudashishikariza abantu batagaragaza ibimenyetso kwambara udupfukamunwa.
