Katherine, CRT (Amanda K, Amy V, Bryan J, Doreen D, Gregory V, Jaime V, Joel L, Lynette L, Ryan M na Tony S) n'abandi bari mu itsinda ry'ubuyobozi (Grant I, Heather W, Jaime V, Janeen U, Lisa S, Robyn A, Ryan M na Toby N).
Angiotensin converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni enzymes ifata ku gice cy'inyuma cy'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
ACE2 ihangana n'ibikorwa bya enzyme ihindura angiotensin (ACE) ijyanye no kugabanya ingano ya angiotensin-II no kongera Ang ((1-7) bigatuma ishobora kuba umuti wifuzwa mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 kandi ikora nk'ikigo cyo kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za koronavirusi zimwe na zimwe.
Ubwoko bw'umuntu bwa enzyme bukunze kwitwa hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 ni zinc irimo metaloenzyme iherereye ku gice cy'umubiri w'umubiri n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 irimo M2 domain ya peptidase ya N-terminal na colectrin C-terminal domain itwara amino acide ya renal.
ACE2 ni ubwoko bw'indimu ya poroteyine 1 y'umuhanda umwe, ifite inzobere ya enzymatic igaragara ku mibiri y'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha no mu zindi ngingo.
Uru rugingo rw'inyuma rwa ACE2 rwinjira mu mubiri binyuze mu wundi muti witwa sheddase, maze poroteyine ivuye muri uwo muti igashyirwa mu maraso, amaherezo ikajya mu maraso.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ihurira ku ngirabuzimafatizo z'ingirabuzimafatizo nyinshi z'umusemburo wa alveolus type II, intanga ngogozi zo mu nda nto, imitsi n'utugingo tw'umushongi n'utugingo tw'umusemburo mu bice byinshi by'umubiri.
Igikorwa cya mRNA ACE2 cyanabonetse mu gice cy'ubwonko cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa striatum, mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa hypothalamus no mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa brain stem.
Uruhare rw'ingenzi rwa ACE2 ni ugukora nk'igihombo cya ACE.
ACE ishyiraho ingufu za angiotensin I mu kugabanya ingufu za angiotensin II.
ACE2 yo ihita ifata phenylalanine ya amino acide karboxylic-terminal ya angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) maze ikayivamo ingufu mu buryo bw'isuku y'amaraso (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora no kwemeza ibindi bice byinshi birimo [des-Arg9]- bradikinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A na ghrelin.
ACE2 nayo igenzura imikoranire ya membrane ya SLC6A19 imena ya amino acide kandi igaragazwa mu ndwara ya Hartnup.
Nk'indwara y'uruhu, ACE2 ikora nk'ikigo cy'ingenzi cyo kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za koronavirusi zimwe na zimwe zirimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, guhuza poroteyine S1 ifata neza SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 ku gice cya enzymatic cya ACE2 hejuru y'urwego rw'ingirabuzimafatizo biganisha ku kwanduza no guhindura virusi na enzymes mu gice cy'imbere kiri hagati y'ingirabuzimafatizo.
Inzira yo kwinjira nayo isaba kwinjiza poroteyine S na TMPRSS2 serine prosthesis, inhibitor ikomeje kwigwaho ubushakashatsi nk'umuti ushobora kuvura. Ibi byatumye bamwe batekereza ko kugabanya urugero rwa ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo bishobora gufasha mu kurwanya ubwandu.
Ariko, amashyirahamwe y'abahanga n'inzego zishinzwe kugenzura inama zisaba gukomeza gukoresha ACE inhibitors n'ubuvuzi bwa ARB.
Isesengura ryagutse n'isesengura rya meta ryasohotse ku ya 11 Nyakanga 2012 ryagaragaje ko "ikoreshwa rya ACE inhibitors rifitanye isano no kugabanuka cyane kwa 34% kw'ibyago bya pneumonia ugereranyije n'ibipimo".
Byongeye kandi, "ibyago byo kurwara ibicurane byaragabanutse ku barwayi bavurwa ACE inhibitors bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara ibicurane, by'umwihariko abafite indwara y'ibicurane n'umutima.
Gukoresha ACE inhibitors nabyo byerekanwe no kugabanya umubare w'abapfa bishwe na pneumonia, nubwo nta cyizere gifatika bifite ku bijyanye n'ibyago byose byo kurwara pneumonia".
Gushyira hamwe kwa ACE2 (rhACE2) mu bantu byatangiye gufatwa nk'uburyo bushya bwo kuvura ibikomere by'ibihaha, kandi bigaragara ko byongera imikorere y'amaraso y'ibihaha n'umwuka wa ogisijeni mu bana b'ingurube bafite indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye ubwoba.
Ubuzima bwa kabiri bwa rhACE2 mu bantu ni amasaha 10 kandi gutangira gukora ni iminota 30 byiyongera ku bikorwa by'ingaruka (tempoh) by'amasaha 24.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe na bumwe bugaragaza ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti wizewe ku bantu badaha agaciro angiotensin ya classique (RAS inhibitors) cyangwa indwara ziterwa no kongera angiotensin II.
Porogaramu ya b'COVID-19 ni porogaramu ya porogaramu igendanwa yagenewe gufasha gukurikirana abantu mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-20, ni ukuvuga uburyo bwo kumenya abantu ("abafite aho bahuriye") bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu wanduye.
Porogaramu nyinshi zikorwa cyangwa zatanzwe hamwe na leta zishyigikiwe mu ntara zimwe na zimwe n'ubutegetsi.
Hari imiterere yo kubaka porogaramu yo gukurikirana abantu bamaze gushyirwaho.
Impungenge z'ibanga zatanzwe, cyane cyane ku buryo bushingiye ku gukurikirana aho porogaramu ikorera.
Ibindi bidashobora kubangamira harimo gukoresha Bluetooth mu kwandika amakuru y'umunyamuryango kuri telefoni ye.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ko bagiye gushyira hamwe imikorere yo gushyigikira porogaramu zishingiye kuri Bluetooth mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu y'imikorere ya Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa ifatanyije na Alipay, yatangije porogaramu yemerera abaturage kureba niba barigeze guhura n'abantu banduye COVID-19.
Ikoreshwa mu mijyi isaga 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapore, porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether iri gukoreshwa.
Porogaramu yakozwe n'umuryango w'ikoranabuhanga wo muri ako gace, ishyirwa ahagaragara nk'isoko ryuguruye kandi izashyikirizwa leta. Macedonia ya Ruguru yashyizeho "StopKorona!", porogaramu ishingiye kuri Bluetooth ikurikira guhura n'abantu bashobora kwandura kandi igaha ibisubizo byihuse abayobozi bashinzwe ubuzima.
Porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itumanaho n'Ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, leta yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abantu iri mu byiciro byiterambere, kandi ko izaba iboneka mu byumweru bike. Porogaramu nk'iyo irateganywa muri Irilande no mu Bufaransa ("StopCovid").
Australia na New Zealand birimo gusuzuma porogaramu zishingiye kuri porogaramu ya TraceTogether ya Singapour na protocole ya BlueTrace. Uburusiya bufite intego yo gushyiraho porogaramu yo kugabanya umubare w'abarwayi bagaragaweho COVID-19 baba i Moscou, igamije kubarinda kuva mu ngo zabo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu mu by'ubwubatsi bw'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, agaragaza ibibazo byinshi bishobora kuvuka mu mikorere ishingiye ku bikorwa, harimo ibinyoma n'ubushobozi buke bwo gukora neza mu gihe ishyirwa mu bikorwa ry'ibikorwa rihagarariye igice gito cy'abaturage.
Mu guhangana n'impungenge z'ikwirakwira ry'ibikorwa by'ikoranabuhanga "coronavirus" biyobya cyangwa byangiza, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku bwoko bw'imiryango ishobora kongeramo porogaramu zijyanye na coronavirus mu bubiko bwayo bwa porogaramu, ikabibuza gusa "abari mu butegetsi" cyangwa imiryango izwi.
Google na Amazon byashyizeho ibihano nk'ibyo.
Abashinzwe umutekano mu buzima bw'abantu bagaragaje impungenge bafite ku ngaruka z'ibikorwa by'ubushakashatsi ku bantu benshi bakoresha porogaramu za coronavirus, by'umwihariko niba ibikorwa by'ubushakashatsi byakozwe mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus bizahagarikwa igihe icyo cyorezo kizaba kimaze guhita.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe arenga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko hakorwa ingamba zo kugabanya ubu buryo bwo kugenzura.
Umuryango watangaje ibintu umunani bisabwa ku mishinga ya leta:
