Ibirebana n'inyongera y'ibikorwa by'ubugenzuzi n'ubugenzuzi bigomba kuba bifite ingingo zishingiyeho;
gukoresha amakuru bigomba kuba mu rwego rwo kwirinda COVID-19;
umutekano w'amakuru n'amazina bigomba kurindwa kandi bikagaragazwa ko byarinzwe bishingiye ku bimenyetso;
Igenzura ry'ikoranabuhanga rigomba kwirinda kurushaho kwangiza ivangura no guca abandi mu muhanda;
